324public: //style
325 void reset_style(bool a_geom = false) {
326 //reset fields that are considered as part of the style.
327
328 //::printf("debug : tools::sg::plotter::reset_style :\n");
329
330 shape_automated = true;
331 shape = xy;
332
333 xy_depth = 0.01f;
334 curve_number_of_points = 100;
335 ////////////////////////////////////////////
336 // CERN-PAW seems to have 0.1F and CERN-ROOT 0.05F.
337 value_top_margin = 0.1f; //percent.
338
339 infos_what = s_infos_what_def();
340 infos_width = 0.3f;
341 //infos height is automatic.
342 infos_x_margin = default_infos_margin(); //percent of width
343 infos_y_margin = default_infos_margin(); //percent of height
344
345 legends_automated = true;
346
347 ////////////////////////////////////////////
348
349 if(a_geom) {
350 float xfac = 1.0F/20.0F; //0.05
351 float yfac = 1.0F/20.0F; //0.05
352
353 // Take PAW defaults :
354 float XSIZ = 20 * xfac; //1 //page width
355 float YSIZ = 20 * yfac; //1 //page height
356 float XMGL = 2 * xfac; //0.1 //left x margin (to data frame).
357 float XMGR = 2 * xfac; //0.1 //right y margin (to data frame).
358 float YMGL = 2 * yfac; //0.1 //low y margin (to data frame).
359 float YMGU = 2 * yfac; //0.1 //up y margin (to data frame).
360 // Axes :
361 float VSIZ = 0.28F * yfac; //0.014 //tick label character size.
362 float XVAL = 0.4F * xfac; //0.02 //x distance of y tick label to data frame.
363 float YVAL = 0.4F * yfac; //0.02 //y distance of x tick label to data frame.
364 float XTIC = 0.3F * yfac; //0.015 //y length of X axis ticks.
365 float YTIC = 0.3F * xfac; //0.015 //x length of Y axis ticks.
366 float XLAB = 1.4F * xfac; //0.07 //x distance of y title to data frame.
367 float YLAB = 0.8F * yfac; //0.04 //y distance of x title to data frame.
368 float ASIZ = 0.28F * yfac; //0.014 // axis title (label) character size.
369
370 float YHTI = 1.2F * yfac; //0.06 //y distance of title to x axis.
371 float TSIZ = 0.28F * yfac; //0.014 //title character size
372
373 float zfac = 1.0F/20.0F; //0.05
374 float ZSIZ = 20 * zfac; //1 //page depth
375 float ZMGD = 2 * zfac; //0.1 //low y margin (to data frame).
376 float ZMGU = 2 * zfac; //0.1 //up y margin (to data frame).
377
378 // Data area :
379 //float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
380 //float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
381 //float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
382
383 width = XSIZ;
384 height = YSIZ;
385 depth = ZSIZ;
386
387 left_margin = XMGL;
388 right_margin = XMGR;
389 bottom_margin = YMGL;
390 top_margin = YMGU;
391 down_margin = ZMGD;
392 up_margin = ZMGU;
393
394 title_to_axis = YHTI;
395 title_height = TSIZ;
396
397 if(shape.value()==xy) {
398 m_x_axis.tick_length.value(XTIC);
399 m_x_axis.label_to_axis.value(YVAL);
400 m_x_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
401 m_x_axis.title_to_axis.value(YLAB);
402 m_x_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
403
404 m_y_axis.tick_length.value(YTIC);
405 m_y_axis.label_to_axis.value(XVAL);
406 m_y_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
407 m_y_axis.title_to_axis.value(XLAB);
408 m_y_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
409
410 //set anyway z axis :
411 //m_z_axis.tick_length.value(YTIC);
412 //m_z_axis.label_to_axis.value(XVAL);
413 //m_z_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
414 //m_z_axis.title_to_axis.value(XLAB);
415 //m_z_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
416
417 m_cmap_axis.tick_length.value(YTIC);
418 m_cmap_axis.label_to_axis.value(XVAL);
419 m_cmap_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
420 m_cmap_axis.title_to_axis.value(XLAB);
421 m_cmap_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
422
423 } else { //xyz
424 m_x_axis.tick_length.value(XTIC);
425 m_x_axis.label_to_axis.value(YVAL);
426 m_x_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
427 m_x_axis.title_to_axis.value(YLAB);
428 m_x_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
429
430 m_y_axis.tick_length.value(XTIC);
431 m_y_axis.label_to_axis.value(YVAL);
432 m_y_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
433 m_y_axis.title_to_axis.value(YLAB);
434 m_y_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
435
436 m_z_axis.tick_length.value(YTIC);
437 m_z_axis.label_to_axis.value(XVAL);
438 m_z_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
439 m_z_axis.title_to_axis.value(XLAB);
440 m_z_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
441
442 m_cmap_axis.tick_length.value(XTIC);
443 m_cmap_axis.label_to_axis.value(YVAL);
444 m_cmap_axis.label_height.value(VSIZ);
445 m_cmap_axis.title_to_axis.value(YLAB);
446 m_cmap_axis.title_height.value(ASIZ);
447
448 }
449
450 }
451
452 title_automated = true;
453 title.value().clear();
454 title_up = true;
455 title_hjust = center;
456
457 ////////////////////////////////////////////
458 colormap_visible = true;
459 colormap_axis_labeling = cells;
460 colormap_attached = true;
461 colormap_axis_visible = true;
462
463 ////////////////////////////////////////////
464 x_axis_enforced = false;
465 x_axis_automated = true;
466 x_axis_min = 0;
467 x_axis_max = 1;
468 x_axis_is_log = false;
469
470 y_axis_enforced = false;
471 y_axis_automated = true;
472 y_axis_min = 0;
473 y_axis_max = 1;
474 y_axis_is_log = false;
475
476 z_axis_enforced = false;
477 z_axis_automated = true;
478 z_axis_min = 0;
479 z_axis_max = 1;
480 z_axis_is_log = false;
481
482 m_x_axis.reset_style();
483 m_y_axis.reset_style();
484 m_z_axis.reset_style();
485
486 ////////////////////////////////////////////
487 ////////////////////////////////////////////
488 ////////////////////////////////////////////
489 number_of_levels = 10;
490 levels.clear();
491 data_light_on_automated = true;
492 primitives_enforced = false;
493 inner_frame_enforced = false;
494
495 ////////////////////////////////////////////
496 // setup styles :
497 ////////////////////////////////////////////
498
499 m_title_style = text_style();
500 m_infos_style = text_style();
501 m_title_box_style = text_style();
502 m_background_style = style();
503 m_wall_style = style();
504 m_inner_frame_style = style();
505 m_grid_style = style();
506
507 m_title_style.color = colorf_black();
508 m_title_style.font = font_hershey();
509 m_title_style.encoding = encoding_PAW();
510
511 m_background_style.back_color = colorf_white();
512 m_background_style.line_width = 0; //no border
513 m_background_style.color = colorf_black(); //border
514
515 m_inner_frame_style.color = colorf_black();
516 m_inner_frame_style.line_pattern = line_solid;
517
518 m_grid_style.color = colorf_black();
519 m_grid_style.line_pattern = line_dashed;
520
521 m_infos_style.font = font_hershey();
522 m_infos_style.encoding = encoding_PAW();
523
524 m_title_box_style.visible = false;
525 m_title_box_style.font = font_hershey();
526 m_title_box_style.encoding = encoding_PAW();
527
528 {tools_vforit(style,m_bins_style,it) {
529 (*it) = style();
530 (*it).modeling = modeling_top_lines();
531 (*it).marker_size = 5; //for profile.
532 }}
533 {tools_vforit(style,m_errors_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
534 {tools_vforit(style,m_func_style,it) (*it) = style();}
535 {tools_vforit(style,m_points_style,it) (*it) = style();}
536 {tools_vforit(style,m_left_hatch_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
537 {tools_vforit(style,m_right_hatch_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
538 {tools_vforit(style,m_legend_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
539
540 }
541
542 void gopaw_reset_style() {
543 {tools_vforit(style,m_bins_style,it) {
544 (*it) = style();
545 (*it).modeling = modeling_top_lines();
546 (*it).marker_size = 5; //for profile.
547 }}
548
549 {tools_vforit(style,m_errors_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
550 {tools_vforit(style,m_func_style,it) (*it) = style();}
551 {tools_vforit(style,m_points_style,it) (*it) = style();}
552 {tools_vforit(style,m_left_hatch_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
553 {tools_vforit(style,m_right_hatch_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
554 {tools_vforit(style,m_legend_style,it) {(*it) = style();(*it).visible = false;}}
555 }
556
557 typedef std::pair<std::string,std::string> style_item_t;
558 typedef std::vector<style_item_t> style_t;
559 bool set_from_style(std::ostream& a_out,const style_t& a_style) {
560 style_t::const_iterator it;
561 for(it=a_style.begin();it!=a_style.end();++it) {
562 const std::string& key = (*it).first;
563 const std::string& sv = (*it).second;
564 //::printf("debug : plotter::set_from_style : key \"%s\" \"%s\"\n",key.c_str(),sv.c_str());
565 //if(key=="reset") {}
566 if(key=="tag") {
567 // key to find back <plotter_style>s.
568 // see also :
569 // xml_style::load_plotter_style()
570 // xml_style::find_plotter_styles()
571
572
573 //width,height,depth : could set from style (for exa for lego).
574 } else if(key=="width") {
575 float v;
576 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
577 width = v;
578 } else if(key=="height") {
579 float v;
580 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
581 height = v;
582 } else if(key=="depth") {
583 float v;
584 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
585 depth = v;
586
587 } else if(key=="left_margin") {
588 float v;
589 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
590 left_margin = v;
591 } else if(key=="right_margin") {
592 float v;
593 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
594 right_margin = v;
595 } else if(key=="bottom_margin") {
596 float v;
597 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
598 bottom_margin = v;
599 } else if(key=="top_margin") {
600 float v;
601 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
602 top_margin = v;
603 } else if(key=="down_margin") {
604 float v;
605 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
606 down_margin = v;
607 } else if(key=="up_margin") {
608 float v;
609 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
610 up_margin = v;
611
612 } else if(key=="title") {
613 title = sv;
614 } else if(key=="title_up") {
615 bool v;
616 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
617 title_up = v;
618 } else if(key=="title_to_axis") {
619 float v;
620 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
621 title_to_axis = v;
622 } else if(key=="title_height") {
623 float v;
624 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
625 title_height = v;
626 } else if(key=="title_automated") {
627 bool v;
628 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
629 title_automated = v;
630 } else if(key=="title_hjust") {
631 hjust v;
632 if(!style_parser::shjust(sv,v))
633 {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
634 title_hjust = v;
635
636 } else if(key=="x_axis_enforced") {
637 bool v;
638 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
639 x_axis_enforced = v;
640 } else if(key=="x_axis_automated") {
641 bool v;
642 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
643 x_axis_automated = v;
644 } else if(key=="x_axis_min") {
645 float v;
646 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
647 x_axis_min = v;
648 } else if(key=="x_axis_max") {
649 float v;
650 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
651 x_axis_max = v;
652 } else if(key=="x_axis_is_log") {
653 bool v;
654 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
655 x_axis_is_log = v;
656
657 } else if(key=="y_axis_enforced") {
658 bool v;
659 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
660 y_axis_enforced = v;
661 } else if(key=="y_axis_automated") {
662 bool v;
663 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
664 y_axis_automated = v;
665 } else if(key=="y_axis_min") {
666 float v;
667 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
668 y_axis_min = v;
669 } else if(key=="y_axis_max") {
670 float v;
671 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
672 y_axis_max = v;
673 } else if(key=="y_axis_is_log") {
674 bool v;
675 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
676 y_axis_is_log = v;
677
678 } else if(key=="z_axis_enforced") {
679 bool v;
680 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
681 z_axis_enforced = v;
682 } else if(key=="z_axis_automated") {
683 bool v;
684 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
685 z_axis_automated = v;
686 } else if(key=="z_axis_min") {
687 float v;
688 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
689 z_axis_min = v;
690 } else if(key=="z_axis_max") {
691 float v;
692 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
693 z_axis_max = v;
694 } else if(key=="z_axis_is_log") {
695 bool v;
696 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
697 z_axis_is_log = v;
698
699 } else if(key=="value_top_margin") {
700 float v;
701 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
702 value_top_margin = v;
703 } else if(key=="infos_width") {
704 float v;
705 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
706 infos_width = v;
707 } else if(key=="infos_x_margin") {
708 float v;
709 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
710 infos_x_margin = v;
711 } else if(key=="infos_y_margin") {
712 float v;
713 if(!to<float>(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
714 infos_y_margin = v;
715
716 } else if(key=="infos_what") {
717 infos_what = sv;
718
719// } else if(key=="legends_visible") {
720// bool v;
721// if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
722// legends_visible = v;
723 } else if(key=="legends_automated") {
724 bool v;
725 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
726 legends_automated = v;
727// } else if(key=="legends_attached_to_infos") {
728// bool v;
729// if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
730// legends_attached_to_infos = v;
731 } else if(key=="legends_origin") {
732 vec2f v;
733 if(!sto(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
734 legends_origin.setValue(v);
735 } else if(key=="legends_size") {
736 vec2f v;
737 if(!sto(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
738 legends_size.setValue(v);
739 } else if(key=="legends_origin_unit") {
740 unit_type v;
741 if(!sto(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
742 legends_origin_unit.setValue(v);
743
744 } else if(key=="shape_automated") {
745 bool v;
746 if(!to(sv,v)) {style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;}
747 shape_automated = v;
748
749 } else if(key=="shape") {
750 if(sv=="xy") {
751 shape = xy;
752 } else if(sv=="xyz") {
753 shape = xyz;
754 } else {
755 style_failed(a_out,key,sv);return false;
756 }
757
758 //legends_string
759 //legends_color
760 //legends_string mf_string
761 //legends_color mf_vec<colorf,float>
762
763 } else {
764 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::set_from_style : unknown key " << key << "." << std::endl;
765 }
766 }
767 return true;
768 }
769protected:
770 void style_failed(std::ostream& a_out,
771 const std::string& a_key,
772 const std::string& a_value) {
773 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::set_from_style :"
774 << " failed for key " << sout(a_key)
775 << " and value " << sout(a_value) << "."
776 << std::endl;
777 }
778public:
779 virtual void render(render_action& a_action) {
780 if(touched()) {
781 //uuu have to look if styles had been touched.
782 update_sg(a_action.out());
783 reset_touched();
784 }
785 m_group.render(a_action);
786 }
787 virtual void pick(pick_action& a_action) {
788 if(touched()) {
789 //uuu have to look if styles had been touched.
790 update_sg(a_action.out());
791 reset_touched();
792 }
793 nodekit_pick(a_action,m_group,this);
794 }
795 virtual void search(search_action& a_action) {
796 node::search(a_action);
797 if(a_action.done()) return;
798 if(touched()) {
799 update_sg(a_action.out());
800 reset_touched();
801 }
802 m_group.search(a_action);
803 }
804 virtual void bbox(bbox_action& a_action) {
805 if(touched()) {
806 update_sg(a_action.out());
807 reset_touched();
808 }
809 m_group.bbox(a_action);
810 }
811
812 virtual bool write(write_action& a_action) {
813 if(touched()) {
814 //uuu have to look if styles had been touched.
815 update_sg(a_action.out());
816 reset_touched();
817 }
818 //if(!write_fields(a_action)) return false;
819 return m_group.write(a_action);
820 }

1131public:
1132 size_t number_of_plottables() const {
1133 size_t number = 0;
1134 tools_vforcit(plottable*,m_plottables,it) {
1135 plottable* object = *it;
1136 if(!object) continue;
1137 if(!object->is_valid()) continue;
1138 // take into account all valid plottables, even the one without a representation.
1139 number++;
1140 }
1141 return number;
1142 }
1143
1144#define TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(a__what) \
1145 size_t number_of_plotted_##a__what##s() const {\
1146 size_t number = 0;\
1147 tools_vforcit(plottable*,m_plottables,it) {\
1148 plottable* object = *it;\
1149 if(!object) continue;\
1150 if(!object->is_valid()) continue;\
1151 if(safe_cast<plottable,a__what>(*object)) number++;\
1152 }\
1153 return number;\
1154 }
1155
1156 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(bins1D)
1157 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(bins2D)
1158 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(points2D)
1159 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(points3D)
1160 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(func1D)
1161 TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF(func2D)
1162
1163#undef TOOLS_SG_PLOTTER_NUMBER_OF
1164
1165 void plotted_object_names(std::vector<std::string>& a_names) const {
1166 a_names.clear();
1167 tools_vforcit(plottable*,m_plottables,it) {
1168 plottable* object = *it;
1169 if(!object) continue;
1170 if(!object->is_valid()) continue;
1171 // take into account all valid plottables, even the one without a representation.
1172 a_names.push_back(object->name());
1173 }
1174 }

1185 //WARNING : it takes ownership of a_p object.
1186 m_plottables.push_back(a_p);
1187 touch();
1188 }
1189
1190 void prep_plottable(plottable* a_p) {
1191 //WARNING : it takes ownership of a_p object.
1192 m_plottables.insert(m_plottables.begin(),a_p);
1193 touch();
1194 }
1195
1196 void transfer_plottables(std::vector<plottable*>& a_to) {
1197 a_to = m_plottables;
1198 m_plottables.clear(); //do not delete plottables !
1199 touch();
1200 }
1201
1202 template <class T>
1203 bool remove_plottables() {
1204 bool found = false;
1205 std::vector<plottable*>::iterator it;
1206 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();) {
1207 plottable* object = *it;
1208 if(object && safe_cast<plottable,T>(*object)) {
1209 it = m_plottables.erase(it);
1210 delete object;
1211 found = true;
1212 } else {
1213 it++;
1214 }
1215 }
1216 if(found) touch();
1217 return found;
1218 }

1220 void add_primitive(plotprim* a_prim) {m_primitives.push_back(a_prim);touch();}

1223 void add_todel(T* a_obj) {
1224 m_todel_group.add(new sg::holder<T>(a_obj));
1225 }

1227 void remove_todels(){
1228 remove_holders<T>(m_todel_group.children());
1229 }
1230 void transfer_todels(std::vector<node*>& a_to) { //used in sg::plots.
1231 m_todel_group.transfer(a_to);
1232 }
1233 void add_node_todel(node* a_node) { //used in sg::plots.
1234 m_todel_group.add(a_node);
1235 }

1356
1357 std::vector<std::string> bins_modelings(size_t a_index) {
1358 update_shape();
1359 if(m_shape==xy) {
1360 size_t ibins = 0;
1361 std::vector<plottable*>::iterator it;
1362 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();++it) {
1363 plottable* object = *it;
1364 if(!object) continue;
1365 if(bins1D* b1 = safe_cast<plottable,bins1D>(*object)) {
1366 //update_bins1D_xy
1367 if(a_index==ibins) {
1368 if(b1->is_profile()) {
1369 std::vector<std::string> opts;
1370 opts.push_back(modeling_points());
1371 return opts;
1372 } else {
1373 std::vector<std::string> opts;
1374 opts.push_back(modeling_boxes());
1375 opts.push_back(modeling_wire_boxes());
1376 opts.push_back(modeling_bar_chart());
1377 opts.push_back(modeling_top_lines());
1378 opts.push_back(modeling_points());
1379 return opts;
1380 }
1381 }
1382 ibins++;
1383 } if(safe_cast<plottable,bins2D>(*object)) {
1384 //update_bins2D_xy
1385 if(a_index==ibins) {
1386 std::vector<std::string> opts;
1387 opts.push_back(modeling_curve());
1388 opts.push_back(modeling_filled_curve());
1389 opts.push_back(modeling_boxes());
1390 opts.push_back(modeling_wire_boxes());
1391 opts.push_back(modeling_solid());
1392 return opts;
1393 }
1394 ibins++;
1395 }
1396 }
1397 }
1398 return std::vector<std::string>();
1399 }
1400
1401 bool xx_2_yy(const vec3f& a_pos,vec3f& a_out) const {
1402 // a_pos is in data frame NDC coordinates.
1403 {float XSIZ = width;
1404 float XMGL = left_margin;
1405 float XMGR = right_margin;
1406 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
1407 a_out[0] = wData*a_pos[0];}
1408
1409 {float YSIZ = height;
1410 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
1411 float YMGU = top_margin;
1412 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
1413 a_out[1] = hData*a_pos[1];}
1414
1415 {float ZSIZ = depth;
1416 float ZMGD = down_margin;
1417 float ZMGU = up_margin;
1418 float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
1419 a_out[2] = dData*a_pos[2];}
1420
1421 return true;
1422 }
1423
1424 bool data_frame_2_vp(const vec3f& a_pos,vec3f& a_vp) const {
1425 // a_pos is in data frame NDC coordinates.
1426 // a_vp is in viewport/screen coordinates (in [0,1]).
1427 {float XSIZ = width;
1428 float XMGL = left_margin;
1429 float XMGR = right_margin;
1430 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
1431 if(XSIZ==0.0F) {
1432 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::data_frame_2_vp","XSIZ is 0");
1433 return false;
1434 }
1435 a_vp[0] = (wData*a_pos[0] + XMGL)/XSIZ;}
1436
1437 {float YSIZ = height;
1438 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
1439 float YMGU = top_margin;
1440 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
1441 if(YSIZ==0.0F) {
1442 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::data_frame_2_vp","YSIZ is 0");
1443 return false;
1444 }
1445 a_vp[1] = (hData*a_pos[1] + YMGL)/YSIZ;}
1446
1447 {float ZSIZ = depth;
1448 float ZMGD = down_margin;
1449 float ZMGU = up_margin;
1450 float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
1451 if(ZSIZ==0.0F) {
1452 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::data_frame_2_vp","ZSIZ is 0");
1453 return false;
1454 }
1455 a_vp[2] = (dData*a_pos[2] + ZMGD)/ZSIZ;}
1456
1457 return true;
1458 }
1459
1460 bool vp_2_data_frame(const vec3f& a_vp,vec3f& a_pos) const {
1461 // a_vp is in viewport/screen coordinates (in [0,1]).
1462 // a_pos is in data frame NDC coordinates.
1463
1464 {float XSIZ = width;
1465 float XMGL = left_margin;
1466 float XMGR = right_margin;
1467 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
1468 if(wData==0.0F) {
1469 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::vp_2_data_frame","wData is 0");
1470 return false;
1471 }
1472 a_pos[0] = (a_vp[0]*XSIZ - XMGL)/wData;}
1473
1474 {float YSIZ = height;
1475 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
1476 float YMGU = top_margin;
1477 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
1478 if(hData==0.0F) {
1479 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::vp_2_data_frame","hData is 0");
1480 return false;
1481 }
1482 a_pos[1] = (a_vp[1]*YSIZ - YMGL)/hData;}
1483
1484 {float ZSIZ = depth;
1485 float ZMGD = down_margin;
1486 float ZMGU = up_margin;
1487 float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
1488 if(dData==0.0F) {
1489 //SoDebugError::postInfo("inlib::sg;:plotter::vp_2_data_frame","dData is 0");
1490 return false;
1491 }
1492 a_pos[2] = (a_vp[2]*ZSIZ - ZMGD)/dData;}
1493
1494 return true;
1495 }
1496
1497 bool data_frame_2_axis(const vec3f& aDF,vec3f& a_pos) const {
1498 // aDF is in data area coordinates. In [0,1][0,1][0,1].
1499 // a_pos is in axes coordinates.
1500
1501 // Assume that axes min,max,is_log are up to date.
1502
1503 {float mn = m_x_axis.minimum_value;
1504 float mx = m_x_axis.maximum_value;
1505 bool lg = m_x_axis.is_log;
1506 if(lg) {
1507 mn = fpow(10,mn);
1508 mx = fpow(10,mx);
1509 }
1510 a_pos[0] = verify_log_inv(aDF[0],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1511
1512 {float mn = m_y_axis.minimum_value;
1513 float mx = m_y_axis.maximum_value;
1514 bool lg = m_y_axis.is_log;
1515 if(lg) {
1516 mn = fpow(10,mn);
1517 mx = fpow(10,mx);
1518 }
1519 a_pos[1] = verify_log_inv(aDF[1],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1520
1521 {float mn = m_z_axis.minimum_value;
1522 float mx = m_z_axis.maximum_value;
1523 bool lg = m_z_axis.is_log;
1524 if(lg) {
1525 mn = fpow(10,mn);
1526 mx = fpow(10,mx);
1527 }
1528 a_pos[2] = verify_log_inv(aDF[2],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1529
1530 return true;
1531 }
1532
1533 bool axis_2_data_frame(const vec3f& a_pos,vec3f& aDF) const {
1534 // a_pos is in axes coordinates.
1535 // aDF in data area coodinate. In [0,1][0,1][0,1].
1536
1537 // Assume that axes min,max,logScale are up to date.
1538
1539 {float mn = m_x_axis.minimum_value;
1540 float mx = m_x_axis.maximum_value;
1541 if(mx==mn) {
1542 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1543 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","x : mn (%g) == mx (%g)",mn,mx);
1544 return false;
1545 }
1546 bool lg = m_x_axis.is_log;
1547 if(lg) {
1548 if(mn<=0) {
1549 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1550 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","x log but mn (%g) <=0",mn);
1551 return false;
1552 }
1553 if(mx<=0) {
1554 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1555 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","x log but mx (%g) <=0",mx);
1556 return false;
1557 }
1558 mn = flog10(mn);
1559 mx = flog10(mx);
1560 }
1561 aDF[0] = verify_log(a_pos[0],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1562
1563 {float mn = m_y_axis.minimum_value;
1564 float mx = m_y_axis.maximum_value;
1565 if(mx==mn) {
1566 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1567 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","y : mn (%g) == mx (%g)",mn,mx);
1568 return false;
1569 }
1570 bool lg = m_y_axis.is_log;
1571 if(lg) {
1572 if(mn<=0) {
1573 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1574 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","y log but mn (%g) <=0",mn);
1575 return false;
1576 }
1577 if(mx<=0) {
1578 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1579 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","y log but mx (%g) <=0",mx);
1580 return false;
1581 }
1582 mn = flog10(mn);
1583 mx = flog10(mx);
1584 }
1585 aDF[1] = verify_log(a_pos[1],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1586
1587 {float mn = m_z_axis.minimum_value;
1588 float mx = m_z_axis.maximum_value;
1589 if(mx==mn) {
1590 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1591 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","z : mn (%g) == mx (%g)",mn,mx);
1592 return false;
1593 }
1594 bool lg = m_z_axis.is_log;
1595 if(lg) {
1596 if(mn<=0) {
1597 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1598 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","z log but mn (%g) <=0",mn);
1599 return false;
1600 }
1601 if(mx<=0) {
1602 //SoDebugError::postInfo
1603 // ("inlib::sg;:plotter::axis_2_data_frame","z log but mx (%g) <=0",mx);
1604 return false;
1605 }
1606 mn = flog10(mn);
1607 mx = flog10(mx);
1608 }
1609 aDF[2] = verify_log(a_pos[2],mn,mx-mn,lg);}
1610
1611 return true;
1612 }
1613
1614 bool axis_2_vp(const vec3f& a_pos,vec3f& a_vp) const {
1615 // a_pos is in axes coordinates.
1616 // a_vp is in viewport/screen coordinates (in [0,1]).
1617 vec3f d; // In data area coodinate. In [0,1][0,1][0,1].
1618 if(!axis_2_data_frame(a_pos,d)) return false;
1619 return data_frame_2_vp(d,a_vp);
1620 }
1621
1622 bool vp_2_axis(const vec3f& a_vp,vec3f& a_pos) const {
1623 // a_vp is in viewport/screen coordinates (in [0,1]).
1624 // a_pos is in axes coordinates.
1625 vec3f d; // In data area coodinate. In [0,1][0,1][0,1].
1626 if(!vp_2_data_frame(a_vp,d)) return false;
1627 return data_frame_2_axis(d,a_pos);
1628 }

1747 void update_layout(){
1748 float XSIZ = width;
1749 float XMGL = left_margin;
1750 float XMGR = right_margin;
1751 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
1752
1753 float YSIZ = height;
1754 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
1755 float YMGU = top_margin;
1756 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
1757
1758 float ZSIZ = depth;
1759 float ZMGD = down_margin;
1760 float ZMGU = up_margin;
1761 float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
1762
1763 {mat4f& mtx = m_layout.mtx.value();
1764 mtx.set_identity();
1765
1766 if(m_shape==xy) {
1767 // in rep primitives (0,0) is the lower left corner
1768 // of the data area square;
1769 mtx.mul_translate(-XSIZ/2+XMGL,-YSIZ/2+YMGL,0);
1770
1771 if(data_light_on_automated.value()) m_data_light.on = false;
1772 vec3f dir(0,0,-1);
1773 m_data_light.direction = dir;
1774
1775 } else { //xyz
1776 //printf("debug : update_layout : X : %g %g %g %g\n",
1777 // XSIZ,XMGL,XMGR,wData);
1778 //printf("debug : update_layout : Y : %g %g %g %g\n",
1779 // YSIZ,YMGL,YMGU,hData);
1780
1781 // global transformation (to have a "lego" layout) :
1782 // translate so that the center of the scene
1783 // is the center of the data area cube;
1784 // then rotate to have lego 3D layout.
1785
1786 mtx.mul_rotate(1,0,0,theta*fdeg2rad());
1787 mtx.mul_rotate(0,1,0,phi*fdeg2rad());
1788 mtx.mul_rotate(1,0,0,-90.0F*fdeg2rad());
1789
1790 // To place as CERN-PAW default.
1791 // In CERN-PAW, it is the projection
1792 // which fits in the (XSIZ,XMGL,XMGR)/(YSIZ,YMGL,YMGU)
1793 // page setup.
1794
1795 rotf r1(vec3f(1,0,0),theta * fdeg2rad());
1796 rotf r2(vec3f(0,1,0),phi * fdeg2rad());
1797 rotf r3(vec3f(1,0,0),-90.0F * fdeg2rad());
1798
1799 rotf r = r1*r2*r3;
1800 mat4f m;
1801 r.value(m);
1802
1803 float xmn = -0.5F*wData;
1804 float ymn = -0.5F*hData;
1805 float zmn = -0.5F*dData;
1806 float xmx = 0.5F*wData;
1807 float ymx = 0.5F*hData;
1808 float zmx = 0.5F*dData;
1809
1810 box3f _box;
1811 float x,y,z;
1812 // zmn face :
1813 {x = xmn;y = ymn;z = zmn;
1814 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1815 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1816 {x = xmx;y = ymn;z = zmn;
1817 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1818 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1819 {x = xmx;y = ymx;z = zmn;
1820 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1821 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1822 {x = xmn;y = ymx;z = zmn;
1823 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1824 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1825
1826 // zmx face :
1827 {x = xmn;y = ymn;z = zmx;
1828 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1829 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1830 {x = xmx;y = ymn;z = zmx;
1831 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1832 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1833 {x = xmx;y = ymx;z = zmx;
1834 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1835 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1836 {x = xmn;y = ymx;z = zmx;
1837 m.mul_3f(x,y,z);
1838 _box.extend_by(x,y,z);}
1839
1840 float xfac = _box.mx()[0]-_box.mn()[0];
1841 float yfac = _box.mx()[1]-_box.mn()[1];
1842 float zfac = _box.mx()[2]-_box.mn()[2];
1843
1844 //cube setup (driven by hData) :
1845 mtx.mul_scale(hData/xfac,hData/yfac,hData/zfac);
1846
1847 mtx.mul_translate(-wData/2,-hData/2,-dData/2); //Applied first.
1848
1849 if(data_light_on_automated.value()) m_data_light.on = true;
1850 {vec3f dir(1,-1,-10);
1851 float dx,dy,dz;dir.value(dx,dy,dz);
1852 mat4f inv;
1853 if(mtx.invert(inv)) {
1854 inv.mul_dir_3f(dx,dy,dz);
1855 m_data_light.direction = vec3f(dx,dy,dz);
1856 }}
1857 }}
1858
1859 {mat4f& mtx = m_data_matrix.mtx.value();
1860 mtx.set_identity();
1861 if(m_shape==xy) {
1862 mtx.mul_scale(wData,hData,1); //z size decided with xy_depth
1863 } else if(m_shape==xyz) {
1864 mtx.mul_scale(wData,hData,dData);
1865 }}
1866
1867 }

2367 m_z_axis.update_sg(a_out); // So that the grid be correct.
2368 m_z_axis.reset_touched();
2369 } else {
2370 if(!nplottables) {
2371 m_z_axis.width = 0;
2372 } else {
2373 update_z_axis_3D();
2374 update_axis(a_out,m_z_axis,m_z_axis_data);
2375 }
2376 }
2377 }
2378
2379 if(nplottables) {
2380 // infos box is done before update_legends()
2381 // because legends may be placed relative to it.
2382 update_infos(a_out);
2383 }
2384 m_legend_sep.clear();
2385
2386 if(!legends_automated) {
2387 m_legend_strings = legends_string.values();
2388 }
2389 update_legends(a_out);
2390
2391 if(title_automated) {
2392 std::string _s;
2393 get_title(_s);
2394 title.value(_s);
2395 title.reset_touched(); //output field.
2396 }
2397 m_title_sep.clear();
2398 if(nplottables) update_title();
2399
2400 m_title_box_sep.clear();
2401 if(nplottables) update_title_box();
2402
2403 m_inner_frame_sep.clear();
2404 if(inner_frame_enforced.value() || nplottables) {
2405 if(m_shape==xy) {
2406 update_inner_frame_XY();
2407 } else {
2408 update_inner_frame_XYZ();
2409 }
2410 }
2411
2412 m_grid_sep.clear();
2413 if(nplottables) {
2414 if(m_shape==xy) {
2415 update_grid_XY();
2416 } else {
2417 update_grid_XYZ();
2418 }
2419 }
2420
2421 m_cmap_axis.width = 0;
2422 m_cmap_cells_sep.clear();
2423 if(m_bins_cmaps.size() && m_bins_cmaps[0] && m_bins_cmaps[0]->valn()) { //major_bins
2424 update_cmap(a_out,*(m_bins_cmaps[0]));
2425 } else if(m_points_cmaps.size() && m_points_cmaps[0] && m_points_cmaps[0]->valn()) { //major_points
2426 update_cmap(a_out,*(m_points_cmaps[0]));
2427 } else if(m_func_cmaps.size() && m_func_cmaps[0] && m_func_cmaps[0]->valn()) { //major_func
2428 update_cmap(a_out,*(m_func_cmaps[0]));
2429 }
2430
2431 update_primitives(a_out);
2432 }
2433
2434 void update_axes_data(std::ostream& a_out){
2435 m_x_axis_data.min_value(0);
2436 m_x_axis_data.max_value(0);
2437 m_x_axis_data.is_log(x_axis_is_log);
2438
2439 m_y_axis_data.min_value(0);
2440 m_y_axis_data.max_value(0);
2441 m_y_axis_data.is_log(y_axis_is_log);
2442
2443 m_z_axis_data.min_value(0);
2444 m_z_axis_data.max_value(0);
2445 m_z_axis_data.is_log(z_axis_is_log);
2446
2447 if(!x_axis_automated) { //def = true
2448 m_x_axis_data.min_value(x_axis_min);
2449 m_x_axis_data.max_value(x_axis_max);
2450 }
2451
2452 if(!y_axis_automated) {
2453 m_y_axis_data.min_value(y_axis_min);
2454 m_y_axis_data.max_value(y_axis_max);
2455 }
2456
2457 if(!z_axis_automated) {
2458 m_z_axis_data.min_value(z_axis_min);
2459 m_z_axis_data.max_value(z_axis_max);
2460 }
2461
2462 bins1D* b1;
2463 bins2D* b2;
2464
2465 func1D* f1;
2466 func2D* f2;
2467
2468 points2D* p2;
2469 points3D* p3;
2470
2471 if(first_bins(b1,b2)) {
2472
2473 if(b1) {
2474
2475 if(x_axis_automated) {
2476 m_x_axis_data.min_value(b1->axis_min());
2477 m_x_axis_data.max_value(b1->axis_max());
2478 }
2479
2480 if(y_axis_automated) {
2481 float mn,mx;
2482 b1->bins_Sw_range(mn,mx);
2483 //m_y_axis_data.min_value(mn);
2484 if(mn>=0) mn = 0; //PAW convention.
2485 m_y_axis_data.min_value(mn);
2486 mx = mx + (mx-mn)*value_top_margin;
2487 m_y_axis_data.max_value(mx);
2488
2489 m_y_axis_data.adjust();
2490 }
2491
2492 } if(b2) {
2493 if(x_axis_automated) {
2494 m_x_axis_data.min_value(b2->x_axis_min());
2495 m_x_axis_data.max_value(b2->x_axis_max());
2496 }
2497
2498 if(y_axis_automated) {
2499 m_y_axis_data.min_value(b2->y_axis_min());
2500 m_y_axis_data.max_value(b2->y_axis_max());
2501 }
2502
2503 if(z_axis_automated) {
2504 float mn,mx;
2505 b2->bins_Sw_range(mn,mx);
2506 m_z_axis_data.min_value(mn);
2507 mx = mx + (mx-mn)*value_top_margin;
2508 m_z_axis_data.max_value(mx);
2509 m_z_axis_data.adjust();
2510 }
2511 } /*else if(f_binsList[0]->getDimension()==3) {
2512 //FIXME : should do something.
2513 } else {
2514 // Unusual case.
2515 }*/
2516
2517 } else if(first_points(p2,p3)) {
2518 if(p2) {
2519 if(x_axis_automated) {
2520 m_x_axis_data.min_value(p2->x_axis_min());
2521 m_x_axis_data.max_value(p2->x_axis_max());
2522 }
2523 if(y_axis_automated) {
2524 float ymn = p2->y_axis_min();
2525 float ymx = p2->y_axis_max();
2526 // For pawex22 ?
2527 //m_y_axis_data.min_value(ymn*1.1F);
2528 //m_y_axis_data.max_value(ymx*1.1F);
2529 m_y_axis_data.min_value(ymn);
2530 m_y_axis_data.max_value(ymx);
2531 }
2532 } else if(p3) {
2533
2534 if(x_axis_automated) {
2535 m_x_axis_data.min_value(p3->x_axis_min());
2536 m_x_axis_data.max_value(p3->x_axis_max());
2537 }
2538
2539 if(y_axis_automated) {
2540 m_y_axis_data.min_value(p3->y_axis_min());
2541 m_y_axis_data.max_value(p3->y_axis_max());
2542 }
2543
2544 if(z_axis_automated) {
2545 m_z_axis_data.min_value(p3->z_axis_min());
2546 m_z_axis_data.max_value(p3->z_axis_max());
2547 }
2548 }
2549
2550 } else if(first_func(f1,f2)) {
2551
2552 if(f1) {
2553
2554 if(x_axis_automated) {
2555 float xmn = f1->x_min();
2556 float xmx = f1->x_max();
2557 if(xmx<=xmn) {
2558 xmn = -1;
2559 xmx = 1;
2560 }
2561 m_x_axis_data.min_value(xmn);
2562 m_x_axis_data.max_value(xmx);
2563 }
2564
2565 if(y_axis_automated) {
2566 //same logic as update_func_xy
2567 float xmn = f1->x_min();
2568 float xmx = f1->x_max();
2569 if(xmx<=xmn) {
2570 xmn = m_x_axis_data.min_value();
2571 xmx = m_x_axis_data.max_value();
2572 }
2573 unsigned int nstp = f1->x_steps();
2574 nstp = nstp <=0 ? curve_number_of_points.value(): nstp;
2575
2576 float df = (xmx - xmn)/nstp;
2577 bool problem = false;
2578 float vmin;
2579 if(!f1->value(xmn,vmin)) problem = true;
2580 float vmax = vmin;
2581 for(unsigned int ibin=0;ibin<=nstp;ibin++) {
2582 float xx = xmn + ibin * df;
2583 float val;
2584 if(!f1->value(xx,val)) problem = true;
2585 vmax = mx<float>(vmax,val);
2586 vmin = mn<float>(vmin,val);
2587 }
2588 if(problem) {
2589 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter :"
2590 << " problem when getting some function value."
2591 << std::endl;
2592 }
2593 m_y_axis_data.min_value(vmin);
2594 m_y_axis_data.max_value(vmax);
2595 m_y_axis_data.adjust();
2596 }
2597
2598 } else if(f2) {
2599 if(x_axis_automated) {
2600 float xmn = f2->x_min();
2601 float xmx = f2->x_max();
2602 if(xmx<=xmn) {
2603 xmn = -1;
2604 xmx = 1;
2605 }
2606 m_x_axis_data.min_value(xmn);
2607 m_x_axis_data.max_value(xmx);
2608 }
2609
2610 if(y_axis_automated) {
2611 float ymn = f2->y_min();
2612 float ymx = f2->y_max();
2613 if(ymx<=ymn) {
2614 ymn = -1;
2615 ymx = 1;
2616 }
2617 m_y_axis_data.min_value(ymn);
2618 m_y_axis_data.max_value(ymx);
2619 }
2620
2621 if(z_axis_automated) {
2622
2623 //same logic as updateFunction_XYZ
2624 float xmn = f2->x_min();
2625 float xmx = f2->x_max();
2626 if(xmx<=xmn) {
2627 xmn = m_x_axis_data.min_value();
2628 xmx = m_x_axis_data.max_value();
2629 }
2630 int nx = f2->x_steps();
2631 nx = nx <=0 ? 20 : nx;
2632
2633 float ymn = f2->y_min();
2634 float ymx = f2->y_max();
2635 if(ymx<=ymn) {
2636 ymn = m_y_axis_data.min_value();
2637 ymx = m_y_axis_data.max_value();
2638 }
2639 int ny = f2->y_steps();
2640 ny = ny <=0 ? 20 : ny;
2641
2642 float dfx = (xmx - xmn)/nx;
2643 float dfy = (ymx - ymn)/ny;
2644
2645 bool problem = false;
2646 float vmin;
2647 if(!f2->value(xmn,ymn,vmin)) problem = true;
2648 float vmax = vmin;
2649 for(int jbin=ny-1;jbin>=0;jbin--) {
2650 for(int ibin=nx-1;ibin>=0;ibin--) {
2651 float xx = xmn + ibin * dfx;
2652 float yy = ymn + jbin * dfy;
2653 float val;
2654 if(!f2->value(xx,yy,val)) problem = true;
2655 vmin = mn<float>(vmin,val);
2656 vmax = mx<float>(vmax,val);
2657 }
2658 }
2659 if(problem) {
2660 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter :"
2661 << " problem when getting some function value."
2662 << std::endl;
2663 }
2664 m_z_axis_data.min_value(vmin);
2665 m_z_axis_data.max_value(vmax);
2666 m_z_axis_data.adjust();
2667 }
2668 }
2669 }
2670 }

2672 m_shape = get_shape();
2673 //uuuu if(shapeAutomated) {

2861
2862 void update_cmap(std::ostream& a_out,const base_colormap& a_cmap){
2863 if(!colormap_visible.value()) return;
2864
2865 size_t valn = a_cmap.valn();
2866 if(!valn) return;
2867 size_t coln = a_cmap.colorn();
2868 if(!coln) return;
2869
2870 float XSIZ = width;
2871 float XMGL = left_margin;
2872 float XMGR = right_margin;
2873 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
2874
2875 float YSIZ = height;
2876 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
2877 float YMGU = top_margin;
2878 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
2879
2880 float hcmap = hData;
2881
2882 {mat4f& mtx = m_cmap_matrix.mtx.value();
2883 if(m_shape==xy) {
2884 mtx = m_layout.mtx.value();
2885 mtx.mul_translate(0,0,_zgrid());
2886 } else {
2887 float ZSIZ = depth;
2888 float ZMGD = down_margin;
2889 float ZMGU = up_margin;
2890 float dData = ZSIZ-ZMGD-ZMGU;
2891 hcmap = dData;
2892 if(colormap_attached.value()) {
2893 mtx = m_layout.mtx.value();
2894 mtx.mul_rotate(1,0,0,90.0F*fdeg2rad());
2895 } else { //OpenPAW
2896 float zz = -depth*0.5f;
2897 mtx.set_translate(-XSIZ/2+XMGL,-YSIZ/2+YMGL,zz); //applied first
2898 }
2899 }}
2900
2901 float w = XMGR*0.3F;
2902 float xx = wData+XMGR*0.1F;
2903 float zz = 0;
2904
2905 float yy = 0;
2906 float h = hcmap/float(coln);
2907
2908 // colored cells :
2909 {m_cmap_cells_sep.clear();
2910 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(new normal);
2911 for(unsigned int index=0;index<coln;index++) {
2912 rgba* mat = new rgba();
2913 mat->color = a_cmap.color(index);
2914 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(mat);
2915
2916 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
2917 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
2918 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(vtxs);
2919
2920 vtxs->add(xx ,yy ,zz);
2921 vtxs->add(xx + w ,yy ,zz);
2922 vtxs->add(xx + w ,yy + h ,zz);
2923 vtxs->add(xx ,yy + h ,zz);
2924
2925 yy += h;
2926 }}
2927
2928 // surrounding box :
2929 {rgba* mat = new rgba();
2930 mat->color = colorf_black();
2931 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(mat);
2932
2933 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
2934 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
2935 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
2936 ds->line_width = 1;
2937 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(ds);
2938
2939 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
2940 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
2941 m_cmap_cells_sep.add(vtxs);
2942
2943 vtxs->add(xx ,0 ,zz);
2944 vtxs->add(xx + w ,0 ,zz);
2945 vtxs->add(xx + w ,hcmap ,zz);
2946 vtxs->add(xx ,hcmap ,zz);
2947 vtxs->add(xx ,0 ,zz);}
2948
2949 if(!colormap_axis_visible.value()) {
2950 m_cmap_axis.width = 0;
2951 } else {
2952
2953 // right axis :
2954 mat4f& mtx = m_cmap_axis_matrix.mtx.value();
2955 mtx.set_identity();
2956
2957 zz += _zoffset()*0.01f;
2958
2959 if(safe_cast<base_colormap,by_value_colormap>(a_cmap)) {
2960 if(colormap_axis_labeling.value()==cells) {
2961 if((valn+1)==coln) { // <col> <num> <col> ... <num> <col>
2962 mtx.set_translate(xx+w,h,zz);
2963 } else {
2964 mtx.set_translate(xx+w,0,zz);
2965 }
2966 } else {
2967 mtx.set_translate(xx+w,0,zz);
2968 }
2969 } else { //grey_scale,grey_scale_inverse,violet_to_red
2970 mtx.set_translate(xx+w,0,zz);
2971 }
2972
2973 mtx.mul_rotate(0,0,1,fhalf_pi());
2974
2975 m_cmap_axis.title = "";
2976 m_cmap_axis.tick_up = true;
2977 //m_cmap_axis.label_to_axis = 0.01F;
2978 //m_cmap_axis.label_height = 0.10F;

3237
3238 static bool bins2D_to_func(const bins2D& a_bins,float a_X,float a_Y,float& a_value){
3239 unsigned int xn = a_bins.x_bins();
3240 float xmn = a_bins.x_axis_min();
3241 float xmx = a_bins.x_axis_max();
3242 unsigned int yn = a_bins.y_bins();
3243 float ymn = a_bins.y_axis_min();
3244 float ymx = a_bins.y_axis_max();
3245
3246 float dx = (xmx-xmn)/xn;
3247 float dy = (ymx-ymn)/yn;
3248 int ibin = (int)((a_X-xmn)/dx);
3249 int jbin = (int)((a_Y-ymn)/dy);
3250
3251 if((ibin<0)||(ibin>=int(xn))) {a_value=0;return false;}
3252 if((jbin<0)||(jbin>=int(yn))) {a_value=0;return false;}
3253
3254 float xx_0 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_x(ibin);
3255 //float xe_0 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_x(ibin);
3256 float xx_1 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_x(ibin+1);
3257 //float xe_1 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_x(ibin+1);
3258
3259 float yy_0 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_y(jbin);
3260 //float ye_0 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_y(jbin);
3261 float yy_1 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_y(jbin+1);
3262 //float ye_1 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_y(jbin+1);
3263
3264 float val1 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin,jbin);
3265 float val2 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin+1,jbin);
3266 //float val3 = a_bins.getBinSumOfWeights(ibin+1,jbin+1);
3267 float val4 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin,jbin+1);
3268
3269 // Interpolate :
3270 vec3f p1(xx_0,yy_0,val1);
3271 vec3f p2(xx_1,yy_0,val2);
3272 //vec3f p3(xx_1,yy_1,val3);
3273 vec3f p4(xx_0,yy_1,val4);
3274
3275 //FIXME : case of (x,y) in (p2,p3,p4)
3276
3277 plane<vec3f> _plane(p1,p2,p4);
3278 vec3f pt;
3279 line<vec3f> _line(vec3f(a_X,a_Y,0),vec3f(a_X,a_Y,10));
3280 _plane.intersect(_line,pt);
3281
3282 a_value = pt[2];
3283 return true;
3284 }
3285
3286 typedef struct {
3287 const func2D* m_func2D;
3288 const bins2D* m_bins2D;
3289 double m_limits[4];
3290 double m_limits_in[4];
3291 bool m_problem;
3292 } SbFunc;
3293
3294 static double bins2D_to_contour(double a_X,double a_Y,void* aData) {
3295 SbFunc* func =(SbFunc*)aData;
3296 if( (a_X<func->m_limits_in[0])||
3297 (a_X>func->m_limits_in[1])||
3298 (a_Y<func->m_limits_in[2])||
3299 (a_Y>func->m_limits_in[3])
3300 ) return -FLT_MAX;
3301 float value;
3302 if(!bins2D_to_func(*(func->m_bins2D),(float)a_X,(float)a_Y,value)) func->m_problem = true;
3303 return value;
3304 }
3305
3306 static double log_bins2D_to_contour(double a_X,double a_Y,void* aData) {
3307 SbFunc* func =(SbFunc*)aData;
3308 if( (a_X<func->m_limits_in[0])||
3309 (a_X>func->m_limits_in[1])||
3310 (a_Y<func->m_limits_in[2])||
3311 (a_Y>func->m_limits_in[3])
3312 ) return -FLT_MAX;
3313 float value;
3314 if(!bins2D_to_func(*(func->m_bins2D),(float)a_X,(float)a_Y,value)) func->m_problem = true;
3315 return take_log(value);
3316 }

3318 void update_bins2D_xy(std::ostream& a_out,
3319 const bins2D& a_bins,
3320 const style& a_data_style,
3321 int a_index,

3325 float a_zz){

3393 sbFunc.m_limits[3] = limits[3];

3396
3397 if(levels.size()) {

3400 for(size_t zi=0;zi<zn;zi++) zs[zi] = levels[zi];
3401 list_contour.set_planes(zs);
3402 } else {

3404 if(zn<=0) zn = 1;
3405 std::vector<double> zs(zn+1);

3446 painting,*(m_bins_cmaps[a_index]),
3447 list_contour,a_box_x,a_box_y,a_box_z,a_zz /*,std::string(sid.c_str())*/);

3461 std::vector<rep_bin2D> bins;
3462 {for(int jbin=ynbin-1;jbin>=0;jbin--) {
3463 for(int ibin=xnbin-1;ibin>=0;ibin--) {
3464 if(hbe && (a_bins.bin_entries(ibin,jbin)<=0)) continue;
3465

3555 void update_func1D_xy(std::ostream& a_out,const func1D& a_func,
3556 const style& a_style,const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz){
3557
3558 //a_out << "debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_func1D_xy : modeling " << a_style.modeling.value() << " :" << std::endl;
3559
3560 if(!a_style.visible) return;
3561
3562 float xmn = m_x_axis_data.min_value();
3563 float xmx = m_x_axis_data.max_value();
3564
3565 unsigned int nstp = a_func.x_steps();
3566 nstp = nstp <=0 ? curve_number_of_points.value() : nstp;
3567
3568 float df = (xmx - xmn)/nstp;
3569
3570 bool problem = false;
3571 std::vector<vec3f> points(nstp+1);
3572 for(unsigned int ibin=0;ibin<=nstp;ibin++) {
3573 float xx = xmn + ibin * df;
3574 float val;
3575 if(!a_func.value(xx,val)) problem = true;
3576 points[ibin].set_value(xx,val,a_zz);
3577 }
3578 if(problem) {
3579 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::update_func1D_xy :"
3580 << " problem when getting some function value."
3581 << std::endl;
3582 }
3583
3584 const std::string& modeling = a_style.modeling;
3585
3586 if(modeling==modeling_points()){
3587 std::vector<float> pts; //npt*3
3588 clip_points_2D(points,a_box_x,a_box_y,pts);
3589 if(pts.size()) {
3590 //a_out << "debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_func1D_xy :"
3591 // << " ptn " << pts.size()
3592 // << std::endl;
3593
3594 separator* sep = new separator;
3595 m_func_sep.add(sep);
3596
3597 rgba* mat = new rgba();
3598 mat->color = a_style.color;
3599 sep->add(mat);
3600
3601/* if(a_style.marker_style.value()==marker_dot) {
3602 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
3603 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
3604 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
3605 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
3606 sep->add(ds);
3607 }*/
3608
3609 add_markers(*sep,pts,a_style.marker_style.value(),a_style.marker_size.value());
3610 }
3611
3612 } else {
3613
3614 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
3615 std::vector<float>& pts = vtxs->xyzs.values(); //npt*3
3616
3617 clip_polyline_2D(points,a_box_x,a_box_y,pts);
3618 if(pts.size()) {
3619 //a_out << "debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_func1D_xy : ptn " << pts.size() << std::endl;
3620
3621 separator* sep = new separator;
3622 m_func_sep.add(sep);
3623
3624 rgba* mat = new rgba();
3625 mat->color = a_style.color;
3626 sep->add(mat);
3627
3628 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
3629 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
3630 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
3631 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
3632 sep->add(ds);
3633
3634 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
3635 sep->add(vtxs);
3636 } else {
3637 delete vtxs;
3638 }
3639 }
3640 }

3642 static double function_to_contour(double a_X,double a_Y,void* aData) {
3643 SbFunc* func = (SbFunc*)aData;
3644 if( (a_X<func->m_limits_in[0])||
3645 (a_X>func->m_limits_in[1])||
3646 (a_Y<func->m_limits_in[2])||
3647 (a_Y>func->m_limits_in[3])
3648 ) return -FLT_MAX;
3649 float value;
3650 if(!func->m_func2D->value((float)a_X,(float)a_Y,value)) func->m_problem = true;
3651 return double(value);
3652 }
3653 static double log_function_to_contour(double a_X,double a_Y,void* aData) {
3654 SbFunc* func =(SbFunc*)aData;
3655 if( (a_X<func->m_limits_in[0])||
3656 (a_X>func->m_limits_in[1])||
3657 (a_Y<func->m_limits_in[2])||
3658 (a_Y>func->m_limits_in[3])
3659 ) return -FLT_MAX;
3660 float value;
3661 if(!func->m_func2D->value((float)a_X,(float)a_Y,value)) func->m_problem = true;
3662 return take_log(value);
3663 }

3930 void get_title(std::string& a_s){
3931 a_s.clear();
3932 bins1D* b1;
3933 bins2D* b2;
3934 func1D* f1;
3935 func2D* f2;
3936 points2D* p2;
3937 points3D* p3;
3938 if(first_bins(b1,b2)) {
3939 if(b1) {
3940 a_s = b1->title();
3941 } else if(b2) {
3942 a_s = b2->title();
3943 }
3944 } else if(first_points(p2,p3)) {
3945 if(p2) {
3946 a_s = p2->title();
3947 } else if(p3) {
3948 a_s = p3->title();
3949 }
3950 } else if(first_func(f1,f2)) {
3951 if(f1) {
3952 a_s = f1->title();
3953 } if(f2) {
3954 a_s = f2->title();
3955 }
3956 }

4007 bins[index].m_ratio = bins[index].m_val/dbins;
4008 }
4009 }}
4010 if(painting==painting_grey_scale) {
4011 m_bins_cmaps[a_index] = new grey_scale_colormap(bmin,bmax,50);
4012 } else if(painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) {
4013 m_bins_cmaps[a_index] = new grey_scale_inverse_colormap(bmin,bmax,50);
4014 } else if(painting==painting_violet_to_red) {
4015 m_bins_cmaps[a_index] = new violet_to_red_colormap(bmin,bmax,50);
4016 }

4030 for(unsigned int ibin=0;ibin<xnbin_1;ibin++) {
4031
4032 float xx_0 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_x(ibin);
4033 float xe_0 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_x(ibin);
4034 float xx_1 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_x(ibin+1);
4035 float xe_1 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_x(ibin+1);
4036
4037 float yy_0 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_y(jbin);
4038 float ye_0 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_y(jbin);
4039 float yy_1 = a_bins.bin_lower_edge_y(jbin+1);
4040 float ye_1 = a_bins.bin_upper_edge_y(jbin+1);
4041
4042 float xx = (xx_0+xe_0)/2;
4043 float xe = (xx_1+xe_1)/2;
4044 float yy = (yy_0+ye_0)/2;
4045 float ye = (yy_1+ye_1)/2;
4046
4047 float val1 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin,jbin);
4048 float val2 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin+1,jbin);
4049 float val3 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin+1,jbin+1);
4050 float val4 = a_bins.bin_Sw(ibin,jbin+1);
4051
4052 faces[facei] = rep_top_face2D(xx,xe,yy,ye,val1,val2,val3,val4);
4053 facei++;

4055 }

4076 //}

4116 float ymx = m_y_axis_data.max_value();

4127 // User limits :
4128 limits[0] = xmn;
4129 limits[1] = xmx;

4131 limits[3] = ymx;

4143 int n = nSec - 2 * 10;
4144 double dx = (limits[1]-limits[0]) /n;
4145 double dy = (limits[3]-limits[2]) /n;
4146 limits[0] = limits[0] - 10 * dx;
4147 limits[1] = limits[1] + 10 * dx;
4148 limits[2] = limits[2] - 10 * dy;
4149 limits[3] = limits[3] + 10 * dy;

4151 sbFunc.m_limits[0] = limits[0];
4152 sbFunc.m_limits[1] = limits[1];
4153 sbFunc.m_limits[2] = limits[2];
4154 sbFunc.m_limits[3] = limits[3];

4164 double zd = (zmax-zmin)/zn;
4165 for(int zi=0;zi<=zn;zi++) zs[zi] = zmin + zi * zd;
4166 list_contour.set_planes(zs);
4167
4168 if(zlog) list_contour.set_field_fcn(log_bins2D_to_contour,(void*)&sbFunc);
4169 else list_contour.set_field_fcn(bins2D_to_contour,(void*)&sbFunc);
4170
4171 list_contour.ccontour::generate();
4172 if(!list_contour.compact_strips ()) {
4173 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::update_bins2D_xyz : clist_contour::compact_strips () : failure." << std::endl;
4174 delete cmap;
4175 } else {
4176 delete m_bins_cmaps[a_index];
4177 m_bins_cmaps[a_index] = cmap; //to visualize the cmap.
4178
4179 matrix* transf = new matrix;
4180 //contour back is at ZZ - 0.01F;
4181 transf->set_translate(0,0,1.02F);
4182 transf->mul_scale(1,1,0.01F); //applied first.
4183 m_bins_sep.add(transf);
4184
4185 style gs;
4186 gs.light_model = light_model_base_color();
4187 //FIXME gs.transparency = 0.3F;
4188
4189 float ZZ = 0.0F;
4190
4191 rep_contour_xy_filled(a_out,gs,painting_by_level,*cmap,list_contour,
4192 a_box_x,a_box_y,a_box_z,ZZ/*,SbString(sid.c_str())*/);

4194 }

4196 } //uniform

4198 }

4513 void update_title(){
4514 if(!m_title_style.visible) return;
4515
4516 if(m_shape==xyz) return;
4517
4518 if(title.value().empty()) return;
4519
4520 // Use the XY layout transform to position the title.
4521 // (Else we would have to compensate the 3D rotation
4522 // in order to bring the title at the right position
4523 // without rotation).
4524 //titleNode->addChild(layout);
4525
4526 rgba* mat = new rgba();
4527 mat->color = m_title_style.color;
4528 m_title_sep.add(mat);
4529
4530 float text_size = title_height * m_title_style.scale;
4531
4532 std::string font = m_title_style.font.value();
4533
4534 if(font==font_hershey()) {
4535 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
4536 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
4537 ds->line_pattern = m_title_style.line_pattern;
4538 ds->line_width = m_title_style.line_width;
4539 m_title_sep.add(ds);
4540 } else {
4541 m_title_sep.add(new normal);
4542 }
4543
4544 float XSIZ = width;
4545 float XMGL = left_margin;
4546 float XMGR = right_margin;
4547 float wData = XSIZ-XMGL-XMGR;
4548
4549 float YSIZ = height;
4550 float YMGL = bottom_margin;
4551 float YMGU = top_margin;
4552 float hData = YSIZ-YMGL-YMGU;
4553
4554 float xx = wData/2;
4555 float yy = hData + title_to_axis;
4556
4557 float zz = _zinfos();
4558
4559 vjust vjust = bottom;
4560 if(!title_up) {
4561 yy = -title_to_axis;
4562 vjust = top;
4563 }
4564
4565 //::printf("debug : %lu : %g %g : text_size : %g : %s\n",
4566 // this,xx,yy,text_size,title.value().c_str());
4567
4568 vec3f TX(1,0,0);
4569 vec3f TY(0,1,0);
4570 add_string(m_title_sep,
4571 font,
4572 m_title_style.encoding.value(),
4573 m_title_style.smoothing,
4574 title.value(),
4575 xx,yy,zz, //vec
4576 TX,TY,
4577 text_size,
4578 title_hjust,vjust,
4579 m_ttf);
4580 }
4581
4582 void update_title_box(){
4583 if(!m_title_box_style.visible) return;
4584 if(title.value().empty()) return;
4585
4586 // same plane than infos, then in front of data and grid.
4587 float zz = _zinfos();
4588 if(m_shape==xyz) zz = depth*0.5f;
4589
4590 float wbox = width*0.3f;
4591 float hbox = height*0.05f;
4592
4593 float xmargin = width*0.01f; //from left border
4594 float ymargin = height*0.005f; //from top border
4595
4596 matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
4597 {float xx = -width*0.5f+wbox*0.5f+xmargin; //at left.
4598 float yy = height*0.5f-hbox*0.5F-ymargin; //at top.
4599 _tsf->set_translate(xx,yy,zz);
4600 _tsf->mul_scale(1,1,_zscale_text());}
4601 m_title_box_sep.add(_tsf);
4602
4603 sg::text* title_box = new sg::text(m_ttf);
4604 title_box->width = wbox;
4605 title_box->height = hbox;
4606 title_box->back_area::color = m_title_box_style.back_color;
4607 title_box->color = m_title_box_style.color;
4608 title_box->font = m_title_box_style.font;
4609 title_box->encoding = m_title_box_style.encoding;
4610 title_box->line_width = m_title_box_style.line_width;
4611 //title_box->front_face = m_title_box_style.front_face;
4612 title_box->confine = true;
4613 title_box->back_area::shadow = m_title_box_style.back_shadow;
4614
4615 title_box->strings.add(title.value());
4616
4617 m_title_box_sep.add(title_box);
4618 }
4619
4620 void get_infos(std::string& a_s){
4621 // return "[<key>\n<value>]\n".
4622 a_s.clear();
4623 const std::string& opts = infos_what.value();
4624 {bins1D* b1;
4625 bins2D* b2;
4626 func1D* f1;
4627 func2D* f2;
4628 points2D* p2;
4629 points3D* p3;
4630 if(first_bins(b1,b2)) {
4631 if(b1) {
4632 b1->infos(opts,a_s);
4633 } else if(b2) {
4634 b2->infos(opts,a_s);
4635 }
4636 } else if(first_points(p2,p3)) {
4637 if(p2) {
4638 p2->infos(opts,a_s);
4639 } else if(p3) {
4640 p3->infos(opts,a_s);
4641 }
4642 } else if(first_func(f1,f2)) {
4643 if(f1) {
4644 f1->infos(opts,a_s);
4645 } if(f2) {
4646 f2->infos(opts,a_s);
4647 }
4648 }}
4649 //look for fit infos :
4650 {std::vector<plottable*>::const_iterator it;
4651 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();++it) {
4652 plottable* object = *it;
4653 if(!object) continue;
4654 if(object->cast(s_tools_sg_fit2plot())) {
4655 if(a_s.size()) a_s += "\n";
4656 std::string _s;
4657 object->infos(opts,_s);
4658 a_s += _s;
4659 }
4660 }}
4661 }
4662

4664 if(m_infos_sep.empty()) return 0;
4665 return (matrix*)m_infos_sep[0]; //WARNING.
4666 }
4667 sg::infos_box* get_infos_node() {
4668 if(m_infos_sep.empty()) return 0;
4669 return (sg::infos_box*)m_infos_sep[1]; //WARNING.
4670 }

4938 void update_legends(std::ostream& a_out) {
4939 //::printf("debug : update_legends : begin\n");
4940 if(m_legend_strings.empty()) return;
4941 if(m_legend_strings.size()!=legends_origin.size()) return;
4942 if(legends_size.size()!=legends_origin.size()) return;
4943 if(legends_origin_unit.size()!=legends_origin.size()) return;
4944
4945 float zz = _zinfos();
4946
4947 {matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
4948 _tsf->mul_scale(1,1,_zscale_text());
4949 m_legend_sep.add(_tsf);}
4950
4951 size_t number = m_legend_strings.size();
4952 //::printf("debug : update_legends : 001 %lu\n",number);
4953 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
4954 const style& _style = legend_style(index);
4955 if(!_style.visible) continue;
4956 //::printf("debug : update_legends : 002 %lu |%s|\n",index,m_legend_strings[index].c_str());
4957
4958 separator* sep = new separator;
4959 m_legend_sep.add(sep);
4960
4961 matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
4962 sep->add(_tsf);
4963
4964 //sg::text* text = new sg::text;
4965 legend* text = new legend(m_ttf);
4966 text->font = _style.font;
4967 text->encoding = _style.encoding;
4968 text->strings.add(m_legend_strings[index]);
4969 text->color = _style.color;
4970 text->marker_style = _style.marker_style;
4971 text->marker_size = _style.marker_size;
4972 text->back_visible = false;
4973 sep->add(text);
4974
4975 //legends_size is in NDC of [0,width][0,height].
4976 float w = width * legends_size[index][0];
4977 float h = height * legends_size[index][1];
4978 text->width = w;
4979 text->height = h;
4980
4981 float xxx = w * 0.5f;
4982 float yyy = h * 0.5f;
4983
4984 if(legends_origin_unit[index]==unit_axis) {
4985
4986 // legends_origin is in axes coordinates.
4987 float x = legends_origin[index][0];
4988 float y = legends_origin[index][1];
4989
4990 vec3f pos;
4991 if(!axis_2_vp(vec3f(x,y,0),pos)) {
4992 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::update_legends : axis_2_vp() failed for x=" << x << ", y=" << y << "." << std::endl;
4993 } else {
4994 //pos is in NDC of [0,width][0,height].
4995 float xx = width * (-0.5f+pos[0]);
4996 float yy = height * (-0.5f+pos[1]);
4997 _tsf->set_translate(xx,yy,zz);
4998 }
4999
5000 } else { //unit_percent
5001 // legends_origin is
5002 // the UR corner of legend region relative
5003 // to UR of plotter region.
5004 float xur = legends_origin[index][0];
5005 float yur = legends_origin[index][1];
5006
5007 vec2f ur(1-xur,1-yur);
5008
5009 float x = width*ur[0] - w;
5010 float y = height*ur[1] - h;
5011
5012 float xx = -width*0.5f + x;
5013 float yy = -height*0.5f + y;
5014
5015 _tsf->set_translate(xx,yy,zz);
5016 }
5017
5018 _tsf->mul_translate(xxx,yyy,0); //applied first.
5019
5020 }

5023 void update_background(){
5024 m_background_sep.clear();
5025 if(!m_background_style.visible) return;
5026
5027 matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
5028 m_background_sep.add(_tsf);
5029
5030 float w2 = width*0.5F;
5031 float h2 = height*0.5F;
5032
5033 float zz = 0; //in xy, then before first data plane at _zoffset()
5034 if(m_shape==xyz) zz = -depth*0.5f;
5035
5036 {rgba* mat = new rgba();
5037 if(m_background_style.line_width) { //there is a border.
5038 mat->color = m_background_style.color; //then border color !
5039 } else {
5040 mat->color = m_background_style.back_color;
5041 }
5042 m_background_sep.add(mat);
5043
5044 m_background_sep.add(new normal);
5045
5046 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5047 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
5048 m_background_sep.add(vtxs);
5049
5050 vtxs->add(-w2,-h2,zz);
5051 vtxs->add( w2,-h2,zz);
5052 vtxs->add( w2, h2,zz);
5053 vtxs->add(-w2, h2,zz);}
5054
5055 if(m_background_style.line_width) { //border
5056 //WARNING : line_width should be in percent of width.
5057
5058 //NOTE : border is done by drawing a front smaller polygon.
5059
5060 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5061 mat->color = m_background_style.back_color; //yes,yes !
5062 m_background_sep.add(mat);
5063
5064 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5065 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
5066 m_background_sep.add(vtxs);
5067
5068 //float d = width*0.005;
5069 float d = width*m_background_style.line_width;
5070
5071 zz += _zoffset()*0.5f;
5072
5073 vtxs->add(-w2+d,-h2+d,zz);
5074 vtxs->add( w2-d,-h2+d,zz);
5075 vtxs->add( w2-d, h2-d,zz);
5076 vtxs->add(-w2+d, h2-d,zz);
5077 }
5078
5079 }

5107 void update_inner_frame_XYZ(){
5108 if(!m_inner_frame_style.visible) return;
5109
5110 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5111 mat->color = m_inner_frame_style.color;
5112 m_inner_frame_sep.add(mat);

5115 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
5116 ds->line_pattern = m_inner_frame_style.line_pattern;
5117 ds->line_width = m_inner_frame_style.line_width;
5118 m_inner_frame_sep.add(ds);
5119
5120 vertices* ls = new vertices;
5121 ls->mode = gl::lines();
5122 m_inner_frame_sep.add(ls);
5123
5124 // z bottom :
5125 ls->add(0,0,0);ls->add(1,0,0);
5126 ls->add(1,0,0);ls->add(1,1,0);
5127 ls->add(1,1,0);ls->add(0,1,0);
5128 ls->add(0,1,0);ls->add(0,0,0);
5129
5130 // z top :
5131 ls->add(0,0,1);ls->add(1,0,1);
5132 ls->add(1,0,1);ls->add(1,1,1);
5133 ls->add(1,1,1);ls->add(0,1,1);
5134 ls->add(0,1,1);ls->add(0,0,1);
5135
5136 // sides along z :
5137 ls->add(0,0,0);ls->add(0,0,1);
5138 ls->add(1,0,0);ls->add(1,0,1);
5139 ls->add(1,1,0);ls->add(1,1,1);
5140 ls->add(0,1,0);ls->add(0,1,1);

5142
5143 void update_grid_XY(){
5144 if(!m_grid_style.visible) return;
5145
5146 unsigned int number = m_x_axis.tick_number + m_y_axis.tick_number;
5147 if(number<=0) return;
5148
5149 bool draw_vertical = true;
5150 bool draw_horizontal = true;
5151 if(m_grid_style.options.value()=="vertical") draw_horizontal = false;
5152 if(m_grid_style.options.value()=="horizontal") draw_vertical = false;
5153
5154 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5155 mat->color = m_grid_style.color;
5156 m_grid_sep.add(mat);
5157
5158 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
5159 ds->style.value(draw_style::lines);
5160 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
5161 ds->line_width = m_grid_style.line_width;
5162 m_grid_sep.add(ds);
5163
5164 float zz = _zgrid();
5165
5166 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5167 vtxs->mode = gl::lines();
5168 m_grid_sep.add(vtxs);
5169
5170 std::vector<float>& pts = vtxs->xyzs.values();
5171
5172 bool is_solid = m_grid_style.line_pattern.value()==line_solid;
5173
5174 if(draw_vertical) {
5175 float _width = m_y_axis.width;
5176 float xx;
5177 {size_t _number = m_x_axis.coords.size();
5178 if(is_solid) {
5179 pts.reserve(_number*6);
5180 for(size_t count=0;count<_number;count++) {
5181 xx = m_x_axis.coords[count];
5182 vtxs->add(xx, 0 ,zz);
5183 vtxs->add(xx, _width,zz);
5184 }
5185 } else {
5186 pts.reserve(_number*100*6);
5187 for(size_t count=0;count<_number;count++) {
5188 xx = m_x_axis.coords[count];
5189 vtxs->add_dashed_line(xx,0,zz,xx,_width,zz,100);
5190 }
5191 }}
5192 if(m_x_axis.is_log) {
5193 size_t _number = m_x_axis.sub_coords.size();
5194 if(is_solid) {
5195 pts.reserve(_number*6);
5196 for(size_t count=0;count<_number;count++) {
5197 xx = m_x_axis.sub_coords[count];
5198 vtxs->add(xx, 0 ,zz);

5322 void rep_bins1D_xy_top_lines(const style& a_style,
5323 const base_colormap& a_cmap,
5324 const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
5325 const rep_box& a_box_x,
5326 const rep_box& a_box_y,
5327 float a_zz/*,
5328 const std::string& aID*/){
5329 painting_policy painting = a_style.painting;
5330
5331 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
5332 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
5333 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
5334
5335 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
5336 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
5337 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
5338
5339 float y0 = 0;
5340 y0 = verify_log(y0,ymin,dy,ylog);
5341 if(y0<0) y0 = 0;
5342 if(y0>1) y0 = 1;
5343
5344 separator* _sep = new separator();
5345
5346 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
5347 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
5348 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
5349 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
5350 _sep->add(ds);
5351
5352 bool empty = true;
5353 colorf clr;
5354
5355 float yp = 0;
5356 size_t xnbin = a_bins.size();
5357 for(size_t index=0;index<xnbin;index++) {
5358 float xx = a_bins[index].m_x_min;
5359 float xe = a_bins[index].m_x_max;
5360 float y = a_bins[index].m_val;
5361
5362 float val = a_bins[index].m_val;
5363
5364 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
5365 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
5366 y = verify_log(y,ymin,dy,ylog);
5367
5368 // Clipping :
5369 if(xe<0) continue;
5370 if(xx>1) continue;
5371 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
5372 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
5373 if(y<0) y = 0;
5374 if(y>1) y = 1;
5375
5376 separator* sep = new separator();
5377 _sep->add(sep);
5378
5379 /*uuu
5380 a_bins[index].fSeparator = sep;
5381
5382 {char s[128];
5383 //::sprintf(s,"%d",index);
5384 sep->setInfos(s);
5385 //::sprintf(s,"/0x%lx",(unsigned long)sep->getInfos());
5386 std::string sid = aID;
5387 sid += std::string(s);
5388 sep->setString(sid);}*/
5389
5390 if(painting==painting_by_value) {
5391 a_cmap.get_color(val,clr);
5392 } else if( (painting==painting_grey_scale) ||
5393 (painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) ||
5394 (painting==painting_violet_to_red) ){
5395 a_cmap.get_color(a_bins[index].m_ratio,clr);
5396 } else {
5397 clr = a_style.color;
5398 }
5399
5400 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5401 mat->color = clr;
5402 sep->add(mat);
5403
5404 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5405 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
5406 sep->add(vtxs);
5407
5408 vtxs->add(xx,yp,a_zz);
5409 vtxs->add(xx,y,a_zz);
5410 vtxs->add(xe,y,a_zz);
5411 if(index==xnbin-1){
5412 vtxs->add(xe,y0,a_zz);
5413 }
5414
5415 empty = false;
5416 yp = y;
5417 }
5418
5419 if(empty) {
5420 delete _sep;
5421 } else {
5422 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
5423 }

5510 void rep_bins1D_xy_boxes(const style& a_style,
5511 const base_colormap& a_cmap,
5512 const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
5513 const rep_box& a_box_x,
5514 const rep_box& a_box_y,
5515 float a_zz //,const std::string& aID
5516 ){
5517 painting_policy painting = a_style.painting;
5518
5519 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
5520 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
5521 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
5522
5523 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
5524 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
5525 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
5526
5527 separator* _sep = new separator();
5528
5529 _sep->add(new normal);
5530
5531 bool empty = true;
5532 colorf clr;
5533
5534 std::vector<rep_bin1D>::const_iterator it;
5535 for(it=a_bins.begin();it!=a_bins.end();++it) {
5536 const rep_bin1D& rbin = *it;
5537
5538 float xx = rbin.m_x_min;
5539 float xe = rbin.m_x_max;
5540 float yy = rbin.m_v_min;
5541 float ye = rbin.m_val;
5542 if(ye<yy) {
5543 yy = rbin.m_val;
5544 ye = rbin.m_v_min;
5545 }
5546
5547 float val = rbin.m_val;
5548
5549 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
5550 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
5551 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
5552 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
5553
5554 // Clipping :
5555 if(xx>1) continue;
5556 if(xe<0) continue;
5557 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
5558 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
5559 if(yy>1) continue;
5560 if(ye<0) continue;
5561 if(yy<0) yy = 0;
5562 if(ye>1) ye = 1;
5563
5564 //FIXME if(ye<=yy) continue; //Else we shall have a tessellation error.
5565
5566 separator* sep = new separator();
5567 _sep->add(sep);
5568
5569 //a_bins[index].fSeparator = sep;
5570 //{char s[128];
5571 //::sprintf(s,"%d",index);
5572 //sep->setInfos(s);
5573 //::sprintf(s,"/0x%lx",(unsigned long)sep->getInfos());
5574 //std::string sid = aID;
5575 //sid += std::string(s);
5576 //sep->setString(sid);}
5577
5578 if(painting==painting_by_value) {
5579 a_cmap.get_color(val,clr);
5580 } else if( (painting==painting_grey_scale) ||
5581 (painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) ||
5582 (painting==painting_violet_to_red) ){
5583 a_cmap.get_color(rbin.m_ratio,clr);
5584 } else {
5585 clr = a_style.color;
5586 }
5587
5588 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5589 mat->color = clr;
5590 sep->add(mat);
5591
5592 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5593 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
5594 sep->add(vtxs);
5595
5596 vtxs->add(xx,yy,a_zz);
5597 vtxs->add(xe,yy,a_zz);
5598 vtxs->add(xe,ye,a_zz);
5599 vtxs->add(xx,ye,a_zz);
5600
5601 empty = false;
5602 }
5603
5604 if(empty) {
5605 delete _sep;
5606 } else {
5607 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
5608 }
5609 }

5714 void rep_bins1D_xy_lines_one(const style& a_style,const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
5715 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz/*,const SbString& aID*/) {
5716 // Draw lines connecting top middle of bins.
5717
5718 //::printf("debug : rep_bins2D_lines_one\n");
5719
5720 int xnbin = a_bins.size();
5721 std::vector<vec3f> points(xnbin);
5722 for(int index=0;index<xnbin;index++) {
5723 float x = (a_bins[index].m_x_min + a_bins[index].m_x_max)/2;
5724 float y = a_bins[index].m_val;
5725 points[index] = vec3f(x,y,a_zz);
5726 }
5727
5728 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5729 std::vector<float>& pts = vtxs->xyzs.values(); //npt*3
5730
5731 clip_polyline_2D(points,a_box_x,a_box_y,pts);
5732 if(pts.size()) {
5733 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
5734 //separator->setString(aID);
5735
5736 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5737 mat->color = a_style.color;
5738 separator->add(mat);
5739
5740 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
5741 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
5742 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
5743 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
5744 separator->add(ds);
5745
5746 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
5747 separator->add(vtxs);
5748
5749 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
5750 } else {
5751 delete vtxs;
5752 }
5753 }
5754
5755 void rep_bins1D_xy_curve_one(std::ostream& a_out,const style& a_style,const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
5756 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz/*,const SbString& aID*/){
5757 //::printf("debug : rep_bins1D_curve_one\n");
5758
5759 size_t number = a_bins.size();
5760 if(!number) return;
5761
5762 double* xs = new double[number];
5763 double* ys = new double[number];
5764 float x,y;
5765 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
5766 x = (a_bins[index].m_x_min + a_bins[index].m_x_max)/2;
5767 y = a_bins[index].m_val;
5768 xs[index] = x;ys[index] = y;
5769 }
5770 tools::spline::cubic _spline(a_out,number,xs,ys);
5771 //tools::spline::quintic _spline(a_out,number,xs,ys);
5772 delete [] xs;delete [] ys;
5773
5774 float xmn = m_x_axis_data.min_value();
5775 float xmx = m_x_axis_data.max_value();
5776 unsigned int nstp = curve_number_of_points;
5777 float step = (xmx - xmn)/nstp;
5778 std::vector<vec3f> points(nstp+1);
5779 for(unsigned int ibin=0;ibin<=nstp;ibin++) {
5780 float xx = xmn + ibin * step;
5781 double val = _spline.eval(xx);
5782 points[ibin].set_value(xx,float(val),a_zz);
5783 }
5784
5785 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5786 std::vector<float>& pts = vtxs->xyzs.values(); //npt*3
5787
5788 clip_polyline_2D(points,a_box_x,a_box_y,pts);
5789 if(pts.size()) {
5790 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
5791 //separator->setString(aID);
5792
5793 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5794 mat->color = a_style.color;
5795 separator->add(mat);
5796
5797 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
5798 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
5799 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
5800 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
5801 separator->add(ds);
5802
5803 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
5804 separator->add(vtxs);
5805
5806 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
5807 } else {
5808 delete vtxs;
5809 }
5810
5811 }
5812
5813
5814 void rep_bins2D_xy_box(const style& a_style,const std::vector<rep_bin2D>& a_bins,
5815 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_bmin,float a_bmax,float a_zz) {
5816 // Draw box of size proportionnal to bin value.
5817
5818 //std::cout << "debug : tools::sg::plotter::rep_bins2D_xy_box" << std::endl;
5819
5820 separator* _sep = new separator();
5821
5822 _sep->add(new normal);
5823
5824 rgba* mat = new rgba();
5825 mat->color = a_style.color;
5826 _sep->add(mat);
5827
5828 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
5829 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
5830 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
5831
5832 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
5833 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
5834 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
5835
5836 bool empty = true;
5837 float range = a_bmax - a_bmin;
5838
5839 std::vector<rep_bin2D>::const_iterator it;
5840 for(it=a_bins.begin();it!=a_bins.end();++it) {
5841 const rep_bin2D& rbin = *it;
5842
5843 float xx = rbin.m_x_min;
5844 float xe = rbin.m_x_max;
5845 float yy = rbin.m_y_min;
5846 float ye = rbin.m_y_max;
5847 float val = rbin.m_val;
5848
5849 float xsize,ysize;
5850 if(range>0) {
5851 // If val = bmax, the box maps the cell.
5852 xsize = (val - a_bmin) * (xe - xx) / range;
5853 ysize = (val - a_bmin) * (ye - yy) / range;
5854 } else {
5855 //If range is 0. ; then all bins that have
5856 // entries have same values. Draw box xdbin * ydbin.
5857 xsize = xe - xx;
5858 ysize = ye - yy;
5859 }
5860
5861 xx = xx + ((xe-xx) - xsize)/2;
5862 xe = xx + xsize;
5863 yy = yy + ((ye-yy) - ysize)/2;
5864 ye = yy + ysize;
5865
5866 xx = verify_log(xx ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
5867 xe = verify_log(xe ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
5868 yy = verify_log(yy ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
5869 ye = verify_log(ye ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
5870
5871 // Clipping :
5872 if(xx>1) continue;
5873 if(xe<0) continue;
5874 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
5875 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
5876 if(yy>1) continue;
5877 if(ye<0) continue;
5878 if(yy<0) yy = 0;
5879 if(ye>1) ye = 1;
5880
5881 //sg::separator* sep = new separator();
5882 //_sep->add(sep);
5883
5884 /*{char s[128];
5885 //::sprintf(s,"%d %d",rbin.fI,rbin.fJ);
5886 sep->setInfos(s);
5887 //::sprintf(s,"/0x%lx",(unsigned long)sep->getInfos());
5888 std::string sid = aID;
5889 sid += std::string(s);
5890 sep->setString(sid);}*/
5891
5892 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
5893 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
5894 //sep->add(vtxs);
5895 _sep->add(vtxs);
5896
5897 vtxs->add(xx,yy,a_zz);
5898 vtxs->add(xe,yy,a_zz);
5899 vtxs->add(xe,ye,a_zz);
5900 vtxs->add(xx,ye,a_zz);
5901
5902 empty = false;
5903 }
5904
5905 if(empty) {
5906 delete _sep;
5907 } else {
5908 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
5909 }
5910 }

6029 void rep_bins2D_xy_solid(const style& a_style,const base_colormap& a_cmap,const std::vector<rep_bin2D>& a_bins,
6030 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz) {
6031 painting_policy painting = a_style.painting;
6032
6033 separator* _sep = new separator();
6034
6035 _sep->add(new normal);
6036
6037 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
6038 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
6039 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6040
6041 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6042 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6043 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6044
6045 bool empty = true;
6046 colorf clr;
6047
6048 std::vector<rep_bin2D>::const_iterator it;
6049 for(it=a_bins.begin();it!=a_bins.end();++it) {
6050 const rep_bin2D& rbin = *it;
6051
6052 float xx = rbin.m_x_min;
6053 float xe = rbin.m_x_max;
6054 float yy = rbin.m_y_min;
6055 float ye = rbin.m_y_max;
6056 float val = rbin.m_val;
6057
6058 xx = verify_log(xx ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
6059 xe = verify_log(xe ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
6060 yy = verify_log(yy ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
6061 ye = verify_log(ye ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
6062
6063 // Clipping :
6064 if(xx>1) continue;
6065 if(xe<0) continue;
6066 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
6067 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
6068 if(yy>1) continue;
6069 if(ye<0) continue;
6070 if(yy<0) yy = 0;
6071 if(ye>1) ye = 1;
6072
6073 if(painting==painting_by_value) {
6074 a_cmap.get_color(val,clr);
6075 } else if( (painting==painting_grey_scale) ||
6076 (painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) ||
6077 (painting==painting_violet_to_red) ){
6078 a_cmap.get_color(rbin.m_ratio,clr);
6079 } else {
6080 clr = a_style.color;
6081 }
6082
6083 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6084 mat->color = clr;
6085 _sep->add(mat);
6086
6087 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6088 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
6089 //sep->add(vtxs);
6090 _sep->add(vtxs);
6091
6092 vtxs->add(xx,yy,a_zz);
6093 vtxs->add(xe,yy,a_zz);
6094 vtxs->add(xe,ye,a_zz);
6095 vtxs->add(xx,ye,a_zz);
6096
6097 empty = false;
6098 }
6099
6100 if(empty) {
6101 delete _sep;
6102 } else {
6103 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
6104 }

6107 void rep_bins2D_xy_random_one(const style& a_style,const std::vector<rep_bin2D>& a_bins,
6108 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_bmin,float a_bmax,float a_zz
6109 /*,const SbString& aID*/){
6110 //::printf("debug : rep_bins2D_xy_random_one\n");
6111
6112 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
6113
6114 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6115 mat->color = a_style.color;
6116 separator->add(mat);
6117
6118/* if(a_style.marker_style.value()==marker_dot) {
6119 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
6120 ds->style = draw_style::points;
6121 ds->point_size = a_style.marker_size;
6122 separator->add(ds);
6123 }*/
6124
6125 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
6126 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
6127 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6128
6129 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6130 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6131 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6132
6133 // Draw for each bins a number of random
6134 // points proportiannal to bins range.
6135
6136 float range = a_bmax - a_bmin;
6137
6138 bool empty = true;
6139 vec3f points[100];
6140
6141 size_t number = a_bins.size();
6142 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
6143
6144 float xx = a_bins[index].m_x_min;
6145 float xe = a_bins[index].m_x_max;
6146 float yy = a_bins[index].m_y_min;
6147 float ye = a_bins[index].m_y_max;
6148 float val = a_bins[index].m_val;
6149
6150 // If range is 0. ; then all bins that have entries
6151 // have same values. Draw one point.
6152
6153 int nmin = 1;
6154 int nmax = 50;
6155 int npt = range>0. ? (int)((val - a_bmin)*(nmax-nmin)/range + nmin):1;
6156 if(npt>0) {
6157 int ipt = 0;
6158 float xdbin = xe - xx;
6159 float ydbin = ye - yy;
6160 for(int count=0;count<npt;count++) {
6161 float xxx = xx + xdbin * (((float)::rand())/RAND_MAX);
6162 float yyy = yy + ydbin * (((float)::rand())/RAND_MAX);
6163 xxx = verify_log(xxx ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
6164 yyy = verify_log(yyy ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
6165 if((xxx>=0)&&(xxx<=1) &&
6166 (yyy>=0)&&(yyy<=1) ) {
6167 points[ipt].set_value(xxx,yyy,a_zz);
6168 ipt++;
6169 }
6170 }
6171 if(ipt>0) {
6172 add_markers(*separator,ipt,points,a_style.marker_style.value(),a_style.marker_size.value());
6173 empty = false;
6174 }
6175 }
6176
6177 }//end for
6178
6179 if(empty) {
6180 delete separator;
6181 } else {
6182 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
6183 }
