6312
6313 void rep_contour_xy(std::ostream& a_out,const style& a_style,painting_policy a_painting,
6314 const base_colormap& a_cmap,clist_contour& a_contour,
6315 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z,float a_zz
6316 /*,const std::string& aID*/){
6317 //a_out << "debug : rep_contour_xy :" << std::endl;
6318
6319 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
6320 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
6321 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6322
6323 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6324 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6325 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6326
6327 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
6328 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
6329 //bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
6330
6331 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
6332 //separator->setString(aID);
6333
6334 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
6335 ds->style.value(draw_style::lines);
6336 ds->line_pattern.value(a_style.line_pattern);
6337 ds->line_width.value(a_style.line_width);
6338 separator->add(ds);
6339
6340 atb_vertices* vtxs = new atb_vertices;
6341 vtxs->mode = gl::lines(); //segments
6342 separator->add(vtxs);
6343
6344 bool empty = true;
6345
6346 for (unsigned int i=0;i<a_contour.get_number_of_planes();i++) {
6347 cline_strip_list* pStripList = a_contour.get_lines(i);
6348 if(!pStripList) {
6349 a_out << "tools::sg;:plotter::rep_contour_xy : problem with contour." << std::endl;
6350 delete separator;
6351 return;
6352 }
6353
6354 //If zlog true, zz is already in log.
6355 float val = (float)a_contour.get_plane(i);
6356 float zz = val;
6357
6358 zz = verify_log(zz,zmin,dz,false);
6359 if(zz>1) continue;
6360 if(zz<0) continue;
6361
6362 colorf _color;
6363 if(a_painting==painting_by_value) {
6364 a_cmap.get_color(val,_color);
6365 } else if(a_painting==painting_by_level) {
6366 size_t icol = a_cmap.colorn() ? (i % a_cmap.colorn()) :0;
6367 _color = a_cmap.color(icol);
6368 } else {
6369 _color = a_style.color;
6370 }
6371
6372 tools_lforcit(cline_strip*,*pStripList,pos) {
6373 cline_strip* pStrip = (*pos);
6374 if(!pStrip) {
6375 a_out << "tools::sg;:plotter::rep_contour_xy : problem with contour." << std::endl;
6376 delete separator;
6377 return;
6378 }
6379 if (pStrip->empty()) continue;
6380
6381 //// putting point at start and end of strip
6382 //// retreiving index
6383 //unsigned int index=pStrip->front();
6384 //double xb=a_contour.get_xi(index);
6385 //double yb=a_contour.get_yi(index);
6386 //// retreiving index
6387 ////glColor4f(0,0,1,.8f);
6388 //index=pStrip->back();
6389 //double xe=a_contour.get_xi(index);
6390 //double ye=a_contour.get_yi(index);
6391
6392 bool first = true;
6393 float xprev = 0;
6394 float yprev = 0;
6395 float xx,yy;
6396
6397 tools_lforcit(unsigned int,*pStrip,pos2) {
6398 xx = (float)a_contour.get_xi(*pos2);
6399 yy = (float)a_contour.get_yi(*pos2);
6400 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
6401 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
6402 if(
6403 (xx<0) || (xx>1) ||
6404 (yy<0) || (yy>1)
6405 ) {
6406 // Throw away this strip :
6407 }
6408 if(first) {
6409 first = false;
6410 } else {
6411 vtxs->add(xprev,yprev,a_zz+zz);
6412 vtxs->add(xx,yy,a_zz+zz);
6413 vtxs->add_color(_color);
6414 vtxs->add_color(_color);
6415 }
6416 xprev = xx;
6417 yprev = yy;
6418
6419 empty = false;
6420 }
6421 }
6422
6423 }
6424
6425 if(empty) {
6426 delete separator;
6427 } else {
6428 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
6429 }
6430 }
6431
6432 void rep_contour_xy_filled(std::ostream& a_out,const style& a_style,painting_policy a_painting,

6434 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z,float a_zz
6435 /*,const std::string& aID*/){
6436 //a_out << "debug : rep_contour_xy_filled :" << std::endl;
6437
6438 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;

6440 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6441
6442 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6443 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6444 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6445
6446 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
6447 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
6448 //bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
6449
6450 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
6451 //separator->setString(aID);
6452
6453 vec3f AB,BC,vcross;
6454
6455 {// Draw background :
6456 sg::separator* sep = new sg::separator;
6457 separator->add(sep);
6458
6459 float zz = a_zz - 0.01F;
6460
6461 colorf _color;
6462 if(a_cmap.colorn()) {
6463 _color = a_cmap.color(0);
6464 } else {
6465 _color = a_style.color;
6466 }
6467
6468 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6469 mat->color = _color;
6470 sep->add(mat);
6471
6472 float xx = xmin;
6473 float xe = xmin+dx;
6474 float yy = ymin;
6475 float ye = ymin+dy;
6476
6477 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
6478 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
6479 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
6480 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
6481
6482 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6483 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
6484 vtxs->add(xx,yy,zz);
6485 vtxs->add(xe,yy,zz);
6486 vtxs->add(xe,ye,zz);
6487 vtxs->add(xx,ye,zz);
6488 sep->add(vtxs);
6489
6490 } // End background.
6491
6492 bool empty = true;
6493
6494 for (unsigned int i=0;i<a_contour.get_number_of_planes();i++) {
6495
6496 cline_strip_list* pStripList = a_contour.get_lines(i);
6497 if(!pStripList) {
6498 a_out << "tools::sg;:plotter::rep_contour_xy_filled : problem with contour." << std::endl;
6499 delete separator;
6500 return;
6501 }
6502
6503 sg::separator* sep = new sg::separator;
6504 separator->add(sep);
6505
6506 //If zlog true, zz is already in log.
6507 float val = (float)a_contour.get_plane(i);
6508 float zz = val;
6509
6510 zz = verify_log(zz,zmin,dz,false);
6511 if(zz>1) continue;
6512 if(zz<0) continue;
6513
6514 std::vector< std::vector<vec3f> > contourVector;
6515
6516 tools_lforcit(cline_strip*,*pStripList,pos) {
6517 cline_strip* pStrip = (*pos);
6518 if(pStrip->size() >2) {
6519 std::vector<vec3f> v;
6520 for (cline_strip::iterator pos2=pStrip->begin();pos2 != pStrip->end();pos2++) {
6521 unsigned int index=(*pos2);
6522 float xx = (float)a_contour.get_xi(index);
6523 float yy = (float)a_contour.get_yi(index);
6524 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
6525 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
6526 v.push_back(vec3f(xx,yy,a_zz+zz));
6527 }
6528 contourVector.push_back(v);
6529 }
6530 }
6531
6532 tess_contour tessContour(a_out);
6533 std::vector<tess_triangle> tris = tessContour.getFilledArea(contourVector);
6534
6535 if(!tris.size()) continue;
6536
6537 colorf _color;
6538 if(a_painting==painting_by_value) {
6539 a_cmap.get_color(val,_color);
6540 } else if(a_painting==painting_by_level) {
6541 int icol = a_cmap.colorn() ? (i % a_cmap.colorn()) :0;
6542 _color = a_cmap.color(icol);
6543 } else {
6544 _color = a_style.color;
6545 }
6546
6547 atb_vertices* vtxs = new atb_vertices; //PAW_C/color.kumac. It needs back face.
6548 vtxs->mode = gl::triangles();
6549 sep->add(vtxs);
6550
6551 for(size_t itri=0;itri<tris.size();itri++) {
6552 tess_triangle& tri = tris[itri];
6553 AB.set_value((float)(tri.pointB[0]-tri.pointA[0]),
6554 (float)(tri.pointB[1]-tri.pointA[1]),
6555 (float)(tri.pointB[2]-tri.pointA[2]));
6556 BC.set_value((float)(tri.pointC[0]-tri.pointB[0]),
6557 (float)(tri.pointC[1]-tri.pointB[1]),
6558 (float)(tri.pointC[2]-tri.pointB[2]));
6559 AB.cross(BC,vcross);
6560 if(vcross.z()>=0) {
6561 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointA[0],(float)tri.pointA[1],(float)tri.pointA[2]);
6562 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointB[0],(float)tri.pointB[1],(float)tri.pointB[2]);
6563 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointC[0],(float)tri.pointC[1],(float)tri.pointC[2]);
6564 } else {
6565 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointA[0],(float)tri.pointA[1],(float)tri.pointA[2]);
6566 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointC[0],(float)tri.pointC[1],(float)tri.pointC[2]);
6567 vtxs->add((float)tri.pointB[0],(float)tri.pointB[1],(float)tri.pointB[2]);
6568 }
6569 vtxs->add_color(_color);
6570 vtxs->add_color(_color);
6571 vtxs->add_color(_color);
6572 }
6573
6574 empty = false;
6575
6576 }
6577
6578 if(empty) {
6579 delete separator;
6580 } else {
6581 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
6582 }
6583 }

6585 void rep_errors_plus_xy(std::ostream& /*a_out*/,const style& a_style,const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
6586 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const std::vector<float>& a_bars,float aZ) {
6587 //a_out << "debug : rep_erros_plus_xy : begin :" << std::endl;
6588 separator* _sep = new separator();
6589 //_sep->setString(aID);
6590
6591 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6592 mat->color = a_style.color;
6593 _sep->add(mat);
6594
6595 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
6596 ds->style.value(draw_style::lines);
6597 ds->line_pattern.value(a_style.line_pattern);
6598 ds->line_width.value(a_style.line_width);
6599 _sep->add(ds);
6600
6601 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6602 vtxs->mode = gl::lines();
6603 _sep->add(vtxs);
6604
6605 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
6606 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
6607 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6608
6609 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6610 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6611 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6612
6613 size_t xnbin = a_bins.size();
6614
6615 for(size_t index=0;index<xnbin;index++) {
6616
6617 //Need all bins modeled for fitting.
6618
6619 float val = a_bins[index].m_val;
6620 float bar_height = a_bars[index];
6621
6622 float bar_min = val - bar_height/2;
6623 float bar_max = val + bar_height/2;
6624
6625 float xx = a_bins[index].m_x_min;
6626 float xe = a_bins[index].m_x_max;
6627
6628 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
6629 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
6630 val = verify_log(val,ymin,dy,ylog);
6631
6632 bar_min = verify_log(bar_min,ymin,dy,ylog);
6633 bar_max = verify_log(bar_max,ymin,dy,ylog);
6634
6635 if(xe<0) continue;
6636 if(xx>1) continue;
6637 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
6638 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
6639 //if(val<0) val = 0;
6640 //if(val>1) val = 1;
6641
6642 float ex = (xe+xx)/2;
6643 //if( (ex >=0)&&(ex <=1) ) { //FIXME : have to clip
6644
6645 float edx = 0.3F * (xe-xx);
6646
6647 if((val>=0)&&(val<=1)) {
6648 vtxs->add(ex-edx,val,aZ);
6649 vtxs->add(ex+edx,val,aZ);
6650 }
6651
6652 if(bar_min >1) {
6653 // do nothing
6654 } else if(bar_max <0) {
6655 // do nothing
6656 } else if(bar_min <0) {
6657 if(bar_max >1) {
6658 vtxs->add(ex,0,aZ);
6659 vtxs->add(ex,1,aZ);
6660 } else {
6661 vtxs->add(ex,0,aZ);
6662 vtxs->add(ex,bar_max,aZ);
6663 }
6664 } else if(bar_max >1) {
6665 vtxs->add(ex,bar_min,aZ);
6666 vtxs->add(ex,1,aZ);
6667 } else {
6668 vtxs->add(ex ,bar_min,aZ);
6669 vtxs->add(ex ,bar_max,aZ);
6670 }
6671
6672 }
6673
6674 if(vtxs->number()) {
6675 m_errors_sep.add(_sep);
6676 } else {
6677 delete _sep;
6678 }
6679 }

6780 void rep_hatch1D_xy(const style& a_style,
6781 const std::vector<rep_bin1D>& a_bins,
6782 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz,
6783 bool a_bar_chart){
6784 //printf("debug : inlib::sg;:plotter::repHatch1D_xy : zz %g barchart %d sw %g\n",a_zz,aBarChart,a_style.stripWidth.getValue());
6785
6786 separator* _sep = new separator;
6787
6788 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6789 mat->color = a_style.color;
6790 _sep->add(mat);
6791
6792 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
6793 if(a_style.strip_width.value()==0) {
6794 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
6795 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
6796 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
6797 } else {
6798 ds->style = draw_style::filled;
6799 //ds->cull_face = true;
6800 }
6801 _sep->add(ds);
6802
6803 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
6804 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
6805 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6806
6807 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
6808 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
6809 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
6810
6811 bool empty = true;
6812
6813 vec3f points[5];
6814 size_t xnbin = a_bins.size();
6815 for(size_t index=0;index<xnbin;index++) {
6816 float xx = a_bins[index].m_x_min;
6817 float xe = a_bins[index].m_x_max;
6818 float yy = a_bins[index].m_v_min;
6819 float ye = a_bins[index].m_val;
6820 if(ye<yy) {
6821 yy = a_bins[index].m_val;
6822 ye = a_bins[index].m_v_min;
6823 }
6824
6825 if(a_bar_chart) bar_chart(a_style.bar_offset.value(),a_style.bar_width.value(),xx,xe);
6826
6827 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
6828 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
6829 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
6830 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
6831
6832 // Clipping :
6833 if(xx>1) continue;
6834 if(xe<0) continue;
6835 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
6836 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
6837 if(yy>1) continue;
6838 if(ye<0) continue;
6839 if(yy<0) yy = 0;
6840 if(ye>1) ye = 1;
6841
6842 points[0].set_value(xx,yy,a_zz);
6843 points[1].set_value(xe,yy,a_zz);
6844 points[2].set_value(xe,ye,a_zz);
6845 points[3].set_value(xx,ye,a_zz);
6846 points[4].set_value(xx,yy,a_zz);
6847
6848 //FIXME : have picking a hatch picks also the bin.
6849
6850 hatcher _hatcher;
6851 _hatcher.set_offset_point(vec3f(0,0,a_zz));
6852 _hatcher.set_angle(a_style.angle.value());
6853 _hatcher.set_spacing(a_style.spacing.value());
6854 if(!_hatcher.set_strip_width(a_style.strip_width.value())) {}
6855
6856 bool res = _hatcher.check_polyline(points,4);
6857 if(res) res = _hatcher.compute_polyline(points,4);
6858
6859 size_t numPoints = _hatcher.points().size();
6860 size_t numVertices = _hatcher.vertices().size();
6861 if((res) && numPoints && numVertices) {
6862
6863 const std::vector<vec3f>& _points = _hatcher.points();
6864
6865 if(a_style.strip_width.value()==0) {
6866
6867 size_t ipt = 0;
6868 tools_vforcit(unsigned int,_hatcher.vertices(),itv) {
6869 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6870 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
6871 for(size_t _index=0;_index<(*itv);_index++) {
6872 vtxs->add(_points[ipt]);
6873 ipt++;
6874 }
6875 _sep->add(vtxs);
6876 empty = false;
6877 }
6878
6879 } else {
6880 size_t ipt = 0;
6881 tools_vforcit(unsigned int,_hatcher.vertices(),itv) {
6882 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6883 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
6884 for(size_t _index=0;_index<(*itv);_index++) {
6885 vtxs->add(_points[ipt]);
6886 ipt++;
6887 }
6888 _sep->add(vtxs);
6889 empty = false;
6890 }
6891 }
6892
6893 }
6894 }
6895 if(empty) {
6896 delete _sep;
6897 } else {
6898 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
6899 }
6900 }

6903 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz){
6904 //::printf("debug : rep_points2D_xy_lines\n");

6907 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
6908

6912
6913 separator* _sep = new separator();
6914

6916 mat->color = a_style.color;
6917 _sep->add(mat);

6927 _sep->add(vtxs);

6933 for(unsigned int index=0;index<number;index++) {
6934 a_points.ith_point(index,x,y);

6949 void rep_points2D_xy_curve(std::ostream& a_out,const style& a_style,const points2D& a_points,
6950 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,float a_zz){
6951 //::printf("debug : rep_points2D_xy_curve\n");
6952 unsigned int number = a_points.points();
6953 if(!number) return;
6954
6955 double* xs = new double[number];
6956 double* ys = new double[number];
6957 float x,y;
6958 {for(unsigned int index=0;index<number;index++) {
6959 a_points.ith_point(index,x,y);
6960 xs[index] = x;ys[index] = y;
6961 }}
6962 tools::spline::cubic _spline(a_out,number,xs,ys);
6963 //tools::spline::quintic _spline(a_out,number,xs,ys);
6964 delete [] xs;delete [] ys;
6965
6966 float xmn = m_x_axis_data.min_value();
6967 float xmx = m_x_axis_data.max_value();
6968 unsigned int nstp = curve_number_of_points;
6969 float step = (xmx - xmn)/nstp;
6970 std::vector<vec3f> points(nstp+1);
6971 for(unsigned int ibin=0;ibin<=nstp;ibin++) {
6972 float xx = xmn + ibin * step;
6973 double val = _spline.eval(xx);
6974 points[ibin].set_value(xx,float(val),a_zz);
6975 }
6976
6977 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
6978 std::vector<float>& pts = vtxs->xyzs.values(); //npt*3
6979
6980 clip_polyline_2D(points,a_box_x,a_box_y,pts);
6981 if(pts.size()) {
6982 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
6983 //separator->setString(aID);
6984
6985 rgba* mat = new rgba();
6986 mat->color = a_style.color;
6987 separator->add(mat);
6988
6989 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
6990 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
6991 ds->line_pattern = a_style.line_pattern;
6992 ds->line_width = a_style.line_width;
6993 separator->add(ds);
6994
6995 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
6996 separator->add(vtxs);
6997
6998 m_points_sep.add(separator);
6999 } else {
7000 delete vtxs;
7001 }
7002
7003 }

7051 void rep_bins2D_xyz_box(const style& a_style,const base_colormap& a_cmap,const std::vector<rep_bin2D>& a_bins,
7052 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z,float a_bmin,float /*a_bmax*/){
7053 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
7054 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
7055 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
7056
7057 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
7058 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
7059 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
7060
7061 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
7062 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
7063 bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
7064
7065 painting_policy painting = a_style.painting;
7066
7067 separator* _sep = new separator();
7068
7069 bool empty = true;
7070 //float range = a_bmax - a_bmin;
7071 colorf clr;
7072
7073 std::vector<rep_bin2D>::const_iterator it;
7074 for(it=a_bins.begin();it!=a_bins.end();++it) {
7075 const rep_bin2D& rbin = *it;
7076
7077 float xx = rbin.m_x_min;
7078 float xe = rbin.m_x_max;
7079 float yy = rbin.m_y_min;
7080 float ye = rbin.m_y_max;
7081 float val = rbin.m_val;
7082 float zz = a_bmin;
7083 float ze = val;
7084
7085 xx = verify_log(xx ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
7086 xe = verify_log(xe ,xmin,dx ,xlog);
7087 yy = verify_log(yy ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
7088 ye = verify_log(ye ,ymin,dy ,ylog);
7089 zz = verify_log(zz ,zmin,dz ,zlog);
7090 ze = verify_log(ze ,zmin,dz ,zlog);
7091
7092 // Clipping :
7093 if(xx>1) continue;
7094 if(xe<0) continue;
7095 if(xx<0) xx = 0;
7096 if(xe>1) xe = 1;
7097
7098 if(yy>1) continue;
7099 if(ye<0) continue;
7100 if(yy<0) yy = 0;
7101 if(ye>1) ye = 1;
7102
7103 if(zz>1) continue;
7104 if(ze<0) continue;
7105 if(zz<0) zz = 0;
7106 if(ze>1) ze = 1;
7107
7108 if(yy>=ye) continue;
7109 if(xx>=xe) continue;
7110 if(zz>=ze) continue;
7111
7112 separator* sep = new separator();
7113 _sep->add(sep);
7114
7115 if(painting==painting_by_value) {
7116 a_cmap.get_color(val,clr);
7117 } else if( (painting==painting_grey_scale) ||
7118 (painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) ||
7119 (painting==painting_violet_to_red) ){
7120 a_cmap.get_color(rbin.m_ratio,clr);
7121 } else {
7122 clr = a_style.color;
7123 }
7124
7125 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7126 mat->color = clr;
7127 sep->add(mat);
7128
7129 /*{char s[128];
7130 //::sprintf(s,"%d %d",rbin.fI,rbin.fJ);
7131 sep->setInfos(s);
7132 //::sprintf(s,"/0x%lx",(unsigned long)sep->getInfos());
7133 std::string sid = aID;
7134 sid += std::string(s);
7135 sep->setString(sid);}*/
7136
7137 float sx = xe-xx;
7138 float sy = ye-yy;
7139 float sz = ze-zz;
7140
7141 matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
7142 _tsf->set_translate(xx+sx/2,yy+sy/2,sz/2);
7143 sep->add(_tsf);
7144
7145 cube* _cube = new cube;
7146 _cube->width = sx;
7147 _cube->height = sy;
7148 _cube->depth = sz;
7149 sep->add(_cube);
7150
7151 empty = false;
7152 }
7153
7154 if(empty) {
7155 delete _sep;
7156 } else {
7157 m_bins_sep.add(_sep);
7158 }
7159 }

7161 void rep_top_face2D_xyz(separator& a_sep,const style& a_style,const base_colormap& a_cmap,
7162 const std::vector<rep_top_face2D>& a_faces,
7163 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z) {
7164 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
7165 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
7166 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
7167
7168 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
7169 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
7170 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
7171
7172 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
7173 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
7174 bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
7175
7176 bool empty = true;
7177
7178 painting_policy painting = a_style.painting;
7179
7180 separator* _sep = new separator();
7181
7182 //draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7183 //ds->style = draw_style::filled;
7184 //ds->cull_face = true;
7185 //_sep->add(ds);
7186
7187 atb_vertices* vtxs = new atb_vertices;
7188 vtxs->mode = gl::triangles();
7189 vtxs->do_back = true;
7190 vtxs->epsilon = 1e-6f;
7191 _sep->add(vtxs);
7192
7193 colorf clr;
7194 vec3f nm;
7195
7196 size_t number = a_faces.size();
7197 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
7198 float xx = a_faces[index].m_x_min;
7199 float xe = a_faces[index].m_x_max;
7200 float yy = a_faces[index].m_y_min;
7201 float ye = a_faces[index].m_y_max;
7202 float val1 = a_faces[index].m_v1;
7203 float val2 = a_faces[index].m_v2;
7204 float val3 = a_faces[index].m_v3;
7205 float val4 = a_faces[index].m_v4;
7206
7207 float val = val1;
7208
7209 val1 = verify_log(val1,zmin,dz,zlog);
7210 val2 = verify_log(val2,zmin,dz,zlog);
7211 val3 = verify_log(val3,zmin,dz,zlog);
7212 val4 = verify_log(val4,zmin,dz,zlog);
7213 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
7214 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
7215 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
7216 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
7217
7218 if(val1<0) val1 = 0;
7219 if(val1>1) val1 = 1;
7220
7221 if(val2<0) val2 = 0;
7222 if(val2>1) val2 = 1;
7223
7224 if(val3<0) val3 = 0;
7225 if(val3>1) val3 = 1;
7226
7227 if(val4<0) val4 = 0;
7228 if(val4>1) val4 = 1;
7229
7230 if((xx>=0)&&(xx<=1) &&
7231 (xe>=0)&&(xe<=1) &&
7232 (yy>=0)&&(yy<=1) &&
7233 (ye>=0)&&(ye<=1) ) {
7234
7235 if(painting==painting_by_value) {
7236 float v = (zlog?take_log(val):val);
7237 a_cmap.get_color(v,clr);
7238 } else if( (painting==painting_grey_scale) ||
7239 (painting==painting_grey_scale_inverse) ||
7240 (painting==painting_violet_to_red) ){
7241 a_cmap.get_color(a_faces[index].m_ratio,clr);
7242 } else {
7243 clr = a_style.color;
7244 }
7245
7246 //if(a_style.area_style.getValue()==SoStyle::EDGED) { //OpenPAW.
7247 //}
7248
7249 //////////////////////////////////////
7250 //////////////////////////////////////
7251 vtxs->add(xx,ye,val4);
7252 vtxs->add(xx,yy,val1);
7253 vtxs->add(xe,yy,val2);
7254
7255 vtxs->add_color(clr);
7256 vtxs->add_color(clr);
7257 vtxs->add_color(clr);
7258
7259 direction(xx,ye,val4,
7260 xx,yy,val1,
7261 xe,yy,val2,nm);
7262 nm.normalize();
7263 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7264 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7265 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7266
7267 //////////////////////////////////////
7268 //////////////////////////////////////
7269 vtxs->add(xe,yy,val2);
7270 vtxs->add(xe,ye,val3);
7271 vtxs->add(xx,ye,val4);
7272
7273 vtxs->add_rgba(clr[0],clr[1],clr[2],clr[3]);
7274 vtxs->add_rgba(clr[0],clr[1],clr[2],clr[3]);
7275 vtxs->add_rgba(clr[0],clr[1],clr[2],clr[3]);
7276
7277 direction(xe,yy,val2,
7278 xe,ye,val3,
7279 xx,ye,val4,nm);
7280 nm.normalize();
7281 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7282 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7283 vtxs->add_normal(nm[0],nm[1],nm[2]);
7284
7285 empty = false;
7286 }
7287 }
7288 if(empty) {
7289 delete _sep;
7290 } else {
7291 a_sep.add(_sep);
7292 }
7293 }

7295 void rep_top_face2D_xyz_line(const style& /*a_style*/,const std::vector<rep_top_face2D>& a_top_faces,
7296 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z/*,const SbString& aID*/){
7297 //::printf("debug : rep_top_face2D_xyz_line\n");
7298
7299 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
7300 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
7301 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
7302
7303 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
7304 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
7305 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
7306
7307 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
7308 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
7309 bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
7310
7311 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
7312 bool empty = true;
7313
7314 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7315 mat->color = colorf_black();
7316 separator->add(mat);
7317
7318 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7319 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
7320 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
7321 ds->line_width = 1;
7322 separator->add(ds);
7323
7324 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7325 vtxs->mode = gl::lines();
7326 separator->add(vtxs);
7327
7328 float zepsilon = 0.02f; //for pawex9.kumac top-left and bottom-right.
7329
7330 size_t number = a_top_faces.size();
7331 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
7332 float xx = a_top_faces[index].m_x_min;
7333 float xe = a_top_faces[index].m_x_max;
7334 float yy = a_top_faces[index].m_y_min;
7335 float ye = a_top_faces[index].m_y_max;
7336 float val1 = a_top_faces[index].m_v1;
7337 float val2 = a_top_faces[index].m_v2;
7338 float val3 = a_top_faces[index].m_v3;
7339 float val4 = a_top_faces[index].m_v4;
7340
7341 //float val = val1;
7342
7343 val1 = verify_log(val1,zmin,dz,zlog);
7344 val2 = verify_log(val2,zmin,dz,zlog);
7345 val3 = verify_log(val3,zmin,dz,zlog);
7346 val4 = verify_log(val4,zmin,dz,zlog);
7347 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
7348 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
7349 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
7350 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
7351
7352 if(val1<0) val1 = 0;
7353 if(val1>1) val1 = 1;
7354
7355 if(val2<0) val2 = 0;
7356 if(val2>1) val2 = 1;
7357
7358 if(val3<0) val3 = 0;
7359 if(val3>1) val3 = 1;
7360
7361 if(val4<0) val4 = 0;
7362 if(val4>1) val4 = 1;
7363
7364 if((xx>=0)&&(xx<=1) &&
7365 (xe>=0)&&(xe<=1) &&
7366 (yy>=0)&&(yy<=1) &&
7367 (ye>=0)&&(ye<=1) ) {
7368
7369 vtxs->add(xx,ye,val4+zepsilon);
7370 vtxs->add(xx,yy,val1+zepsilon);
7371
7372 vtxs->add(xx,yy,val1+zepsilon);
7373 vtxs->add(xe,yy,val2+zepsilon);
7374
7375 vtxs->add(xe,yy,val2+zepsilon);
7376 vtxs->add(xe,ye,val3+zepsilon);
7377
7378 vtxs->add(xe,ye,val3+zepsilon);
7379 vtxs->add(xx,ye,val4+zepsilon);
7380
7381 empty = false;
7382
7383 }
7384 }
7385 if(empty) {
7386 delete separator;
7387 } else {
7388 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
7389 }
7390 }

7392 void rep_top_face2D_xyz_by_level(const style& /*a_style*/,painting_policy /*a_painting*/,const base_colormap& a_cmap,
7393 const std::vector<rep_top_face2D>& a_top_faces,
7394 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,const rep_box& a_box_z,
7395 float a_bmin,float a_bmax/*,const SbString& aID*/){
7396 //::printf("debug : rep_top_face2D_xyz_by_level\n");
7397
7398 size_t ncol = a_cmap.colorn();
7399 if(!ncol) return;
7400
7401 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
7402 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
7403 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
7404
7405 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
7406 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
7407 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
7408
7409 float zmin = a_box_z.m_pos;
7410 float dz = a_box_z.m_width;
7411 bool zlog = a_box_z.m_log;
7412
7413 float zz = a_bmin;
7414 zz = verify_log(zz,zmin,dz,zlog);
7415 float zmx = a_bmax;
7416 zmx = verify_log(zmx,zmin,dz,zlog);
7417
7418 bool empty = true;
7419
7420 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
7421 //separator->setString(aID);
7422
7423 atb_vertices* tris = new atb_vertices;
7424 tris->mode = gl::triangles();
7425 tris->do_back = true;
7426 tris->epsilon = 1e-6f;
7427 separator->add(tris);
7428
7429 colorf _color;
7430 vec3f _point;
7431
7432 float d_z = (zmx-zz)/ncol;
7433
7434 size_t number = a_top_faces.size();
7435
7436 for(size_t icol=0;icol<ncol;icol++) {
7437
7438 //sg::separator* sep = new sg::separator;
7439 //bool sep_empty = true;
7440
7441 _color = a_cmap.color(icol);
7442
7443 for(size_t index=0;index<number;index++) {
7444 float xx = a_top_faces[index].m_x_min;
7445 float xe = a_top_faces[index].m_x_max;
7446 float yy = a_top_faces[index].m_y_min;
7447 float ye = a_top_faces[index].m_y_max;
7448 float val1 = a_top_faces[index].m_v1;
7449 float val2 = a_top_faces[index].m_v2;
7450 float val3 = a_top_faces[index].m_v3;
7451 float val4 = a_top_faces[index].m_v4;
7452
7453 //float val = val1;
7454
7455 val1 = verify_log(val1,zmin,dz,zlog);
7456 val2 = verify_log(val2,zmin,dz,zlog);
7457 val3 = verify_log(val3,zmin,dz,zlog);
7458 val4 = verify_log(val4,zmin,dz,zlog);
7459 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
7460 xe = verify_log(xe,xmin,dx,xlog);
7461 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
7462 ye = verify_log(ye,ymin,dy,ylog);
7463
7464 if(val1<0) val1 = 0;
7465 if(val1>1) val1 = 1;
7466
7467 if(val2<0) val2 = 0;
7468 if(val2>1) val2 = 1;
7469
7470 if(val3<0) val3 = 0;
7471 if(val3>1) val3 = 1;
7472
7473 if(val4<0) val4 = 0;
7474 if(val4>1) val4 = 1;
7475
7476 if((xx>=0)&&(xx<=1) &&
7477 (xe>=0)&&(xe<=1) &&
7478 (yy>=0)&&(yy<=1) &&
7479 (ye>=0)&&(ye<=1) ) {
7480
7481 //////////////////////////////////////
7482 //////////////////////////////////////
7483 {clip<vec3f> clipper;
7484 clipper.add(vec3f(xx,ye,val4));
7485 clipper.add(vec3f(xx,yy,val1));
7486 clipper.add(vec3f(xe,yy,val2));
7487 //val[n] had been z normalized.
7488 float z1 = zz+d_z*icol;
7489 float z2 = z1+d_z;
7490 plane<vec3f> plane_z_bot(vec3f(0,0,1),vec3f(0,0,z1));
7491 plane<vec3f> plane_z_top(vec3f(0,0,-1),vec3f(0,0,z2));
7492 clipper.execute(plane_z_bot);
7493 clipper.execute(plane_z_top);
7494
7495 const std::vector<vec3f>& result = clipper.result();
7496 if(result.size()) {
7497 plane<vec3f> plane1(vec3f(xx,ye,val4),vec3f(xx,yy,val1),vec3f(xe,yy,val2));
7498 if(result.size()==3) {
7499 tools_vforcit(vec3f,result,it) {
7500 tris->add(*it);
7501 tris->add_color(_color);
7502 tris->add_normal(plane1.normal());
7503 }
7504 } else {
7505 atb_vertices* vtxs = new atb_vertices; //FIXME : ouch! optimize.
7506 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
7507 vtxs->do_back = true;
7508 vtxs->epsilon = 1e-6f;
7509 separator->add(vtxs);
7510 tools_vforcit(vec3f,result,it) {
7511 vtxs->add(*it);
7512 vtxs->add_color(_color);
7513 vtxs->add_normal(plane1.normal());
7514 }
7515 }
7516 empty = false;
7517 //sep_empty = false;
7518 }}
7519
7520 //////////////////////////////////////
7521 //////////////////////////////////////
7522 {clip<vec3f> clipper;
7523 clipper.add(vec3f(xe,yy,val2));
7524 clipper.add(vec3f(xe,ye,val3));
7525 clipper.add(vec3f(xx,ye,val4));
7526 //val[n] had been z normalized.
7527 float z1 = zz+d_z*icol;
7528 float z2 = z1+d_z;
7529 plane<vec3f> plane_z_bot(vec3f(0,0,1),vec3f(0,0,z1));
7530 plane<vec3f> plane_z_top(vec3f(0,0,-1),vec3f(0,0,z2));
7531 clipper.execute(plane_z_bot);
7532 clipper.execute(plane_z_top);
7533
7534 const std::vector<vec3f>& result = clipper.result();
7535 if(result.size()) {
7536 plane<vec3f> plane2(vec3f(xe,yy,val2),vec3f(xe,ye,val3),vec3f(xx,ye,val4));
7537 if(result.size()==3) {
7538 tools_vforcit(vec3f,result,it) {
7539 tris->add(*it);
7540 tris->add_color(_color);
7541 tris->add_normal(plane2.normal());
7542 }
7543 } else {
7544 atb_vertices* vtxs = new atb_vertices; //FIXME : ouch! optimize.
7545 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
7546 vtxs->do_back = true;
7547 vtxs->epsilon = 1e-6f;
7548 separator->add(vtxs);
7549 tools_vforcit(vec3f,result,it) {
7550 vtxs->add(*it);
7551 vtxs->add_color(_color);
7552 vtxs->add_normal(plane2.normal());
7553 }
7554 }
7555 empty = false;
7556 //sep_empty = false;
7557 }}
7558 }
7559
7560 } //index faces
7561
7562 //if(sep_empty) {
7563 // delete sep;
7564 //} else {
7565 // separator->add(sep);
7566 //}
7567
7568 } //icol
7569
7570 if(empty) {
7571 delete separator;
7572 } else {
7573 m_bins_sep.add(separator);
7574 }
7575 }

7577 // for OpenPAW /GRAPHICS/PRIMITIVES/TEXT
7578 // for OpenPAW /GRAPHICS/PRIMITIVES/ITX
7579 void update_primitive_text(const plottable_text& a_obj){
7580 float z = xy_depth.value()*1.1F;
7581
7582 vec3f pos;
7583 axis_2_data_frame(vec3f(a_obj.m_X,a_obj.m_Y,z),pos); //FIXME return FALSE
7584
7585 xx_2_yy(pos,pos);
7586
7587 separator* sep = new separator;
7588
7589 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7590 mat->color = a_obj.m_TXCI;
7591 sep->add(mat);
7592
7593 matrix* _tsf = new matrix;
7594 _tsf->set_translate(pos);
7595 _tsf->mul_rotate(0,0,1,a_obj.m_ANGLE*fpi()/180.0f);
7596 _tsf->mul_scale(a_obj.m_SCALE,a_obj.m_SCALE,1);
7597 _tsf->mul_scale(a_obj.m_SIZE,a_obj.m_SIZE,1);
7598 sep->add(_tsf);
7599
7600 //SIZE is in page coordinate YSIZ.
7601 //float YSIZ = height.value();
7602 //if(YSIZ<=0) YSIZ = 1;
7603
7604 //::printf("debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_primitive_text : %s : X %g Y %g : SCALE %g SIZE %g : pos %g %g %g\n",
7605 // a_obj.m_TEXT.c_str(),a_obj.m_X,a_obj.m_Y,a_obj.m_SCALE,a_obj.m_SIZE,
7606 // pos[0],pos[1],pos[2]);
7607
7608 if(a_obj.m_FONT==font_hershey()) {
7609 //::printf("debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_primitive_text : hershey\n");
7610 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7611 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
7612 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
7613 ds->line_width = 1;
7614 //ds->line_pattern = m_title_style.line_pattern;
7615 //ds->line_width = m_title_style.line_width;
7616 sep->add(ds);
7617
7618 text_hershey* text = new text_hershey;
7619 text->encoding = "PAW";
7620 text->strings.add(a_obj.m_TEXT);
7621 if(a_obj.m_JUST=='R') {
7622 text->hjust = right;
7623 } else if(a_obj.m_JUST=='C') {
7624 text->hjust = center;
7625 } else {
7626 text->hjust = left;
7627 }
7628 sep->add(text);
7629
7630 } else {
7631 //::printf("debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_primitive_text : freetype\n");
7632 base_freetype* text = base_freetype::create(m_ttf);
7633
7634 text->font = a_obj.m_FONT;
7635
7636 //text->encoding = "PAW"
7637 //text->smooting = a_obj.m_SMOOTHING;
7638 //text->hinting = a_obj.m_HINTING;
7639 text->strings.add(a_obj.m_TEXT);
7640 //text->hjust.value(a_hjust);
7641 //text->vjust.value(a_vjust);
7642
7643 sep->add(text);
7644 }
7645
7646 m_primitives_sep.add(sep);
7647 }
7648
7649 // for OpenPAW /GRAPHICS/PRIMITIVES/BOX
7650 void PAW_hatch(int aHTYP,hatching_policy& a_policy,float& a_spacing,float& a_angle_right,float& a_angle_left) {
7651 // PAW hatching encoding (paw.pdf 1.14(1992) p 174) :
7652
7653 a_policy = hatching_none;
7654 a_spacing = 0;
7655 a_angle_right = 0;
7656 a_angle_left = 0;
7657
7658 int code = aHTYP;
7659 if(code==0) return;
7660
7661 // From PAW FAQ web page.
7662 // special code from code [1,25]
7663 if(code==1) {
7664 a_policy = hatching_left_and_right;
7665 a_spacing = 0.04F;
7666 a_angle_right = 3.0F*fpi()/4.0F;
7667 a_angle_left = fpi()/4.0F;
7668 return;
7669 } else if(code==2) {
7670 a_policy = hatching_left_and_right;
7671 a_spacing = 0.08F;
7672 a_angle_right = 3.0F*fpi()/4.0F;
7673 a_angle_left = fpi()/4.0F;
7674 return;
7675 } else if(code==3) {
7676 a_policy = hatching_left_and_right;
7677 a_spacing = 1.6f*0.07F; //cooking
7678 a_angle_right = 3.0F*fpi()/4.0F;
7679 a_angle_left = fpi()/4.0F;
7680 return;
7681 } else if(code==4) {
7682 code = 354;
7683 } else if(code==5) {
7684 code = 345;
7685 } else if(code==6) {
7686 code = 359;
7687 } else if(code==7) {
7688 code = 350;
7689 } else if(code<=25) {
7690 //FIXME : seems to be done with patterns.
7691 a_policy = hatching_none;
7692 return;
7693 } else if(code<=99) {
7694 //FIXME
7695 a_policy = hatching_none;
7696 return;
7697 }
7698
7699 //code >=100
7700
7701 // code = ijk
7702
7703 int i = code / 100;
7704 int j = (code - i * 100)/10;
7705 int k = code - i * 100 - j * 10;
7706
7707 // j-hatching on rightHatchStyle :
7708 // k-hatching on leftHatchStyle :
7709
7710 if((j==5)&&(k==5))
7711 a_policy = hatching_none;
7712 else if((j!=5)&&(k==5))
7713 a_policy = hatching_right;
7714 else if((j==5)&&(k!=5))
7715 a_policy = hatching_left;
7716 else if((j!=5)&&(k!=5))
7717 a_policy = hatching_left_and_right;
7718
7719 unsigned int NY = 1;
7720
7721 a_spacing = float(NY) * float(i) * 0.07F; //cooking
7722
7723 if(j!=5) {
7724 float angle = float(j==4?45:j*10);
7725 angle = 180.0F - angle;
7726 angle *= fpi() / 180.0F;
7727
7728 a_angle_right = angle;
7729 }
7730
7731 if(k!=5) {
7732 float angle = float(k==4?45:k*10);
7733 angle *= fpi() / 180.0F;
7734 a_angle_left = angle;
7735 }
7736
7737 }
7738
7739 void rep_box_hatch(separator& a_parent,float a_spacing,float a_angle,float a_strip_width,
7740 float xx,float yy,float xe,float ye,float a_zz){
7741
7742 //printf("debug : SoPlotter::repHatch1D_xy : zz %g\n",a_zz);
7743 sg::separator* separator = new sg::separator;
7744
7745 bool empty = true;
7746
7747 vec3f points[5];
7748
7749 points[0].set_value(xx,yy,a_zz);
7750 points[1].set_value(xe,yy,a_zz);
7751 points[2].set_value(xe,ye,a_zz);
7752 points[3].set_value(xx,ye,a_zz);
7753 points[4].set_value(xx,yy,a_zz);
7754
7755 //We can have multiple hatching for a bins ; have a separator :
7756 hatcher _hatcher;
7757 _hatcher.set_offset_point(vec3f(0,0,a_zz));
7758 _hatcher.set_angle(a_angle);
7759 _hatcher.set_spacing(a_spacing);
7760 if(!_hatcher.set_strip_width(a_strip_width)) {}
7761
7762 bool res = _hatcher.check_polyline(points,4);
7763 if(res) res = _hatcher.compute_polyline(points,4);
7764
7765 size_t numPoints = _hatcher.points().size();
7766 size_t numVertices = _hatcher.vertices().size();
7767 if((res) && numPoints && numVertices) {
7768
7769 const std::vector<vec3f>& _points = _hatcher.points();
7770
7771 if(a_strip_width==0) {
7772 size_t ipt = 0;
7773 tools_vforcit(unsigned int,_hatcher.vertices(),itv) {
7774 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7775 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
7776 for(size_t index=0;index<(*itv);index++) {
7777 vtxs->add(_points[ipt]);
7778 ipt++;
7779 }
7780 separator->add(vtxs);
7781 empty = false;
7782 }
7783
7784 } else {
7785 size_t ipt = 0;
7786 tools_vforcit(unsigned int,_hatcher.vertices(),itv) {
7787 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7788 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
7789 for(size_t index=0;index<(*itv);index++) {
7790 vtxs->add(_points[ipt]);
7791 ipt++;
7792 }
7793 separator->add(vtxs);
7794 empty = false;
7795 }
7796 }
7797
7798 empty = false;
7799 }
7800
7801 if(empty) {
7802 delete separator;
7803 } else {
7804 a_parent.add(separator);
7805 }
7806 }
7807
7808 void update_primitive_box(std::ostream& a_out,const plottable_box& a_obj){
7809
7810 float z = xy_depth.value()*1.1F;
7811
7812 vec3f pos1;
7813 axis_2_data_frame(vec3f(a_obj.m_X1,a_obj.m_Y1,z),pos1);
7814 xx_2_yy(pos1,pos1);
7815
7816 vec3f pos2;
7817 axis_2_data_frame(vec3f(a_obj.m_X2,a_obj.m_Y2,z),pos2);
7818 xx_2_yy(pos2,pos2);
7819
7820 z = pos1[2];
7821
7822// ::printf("debug : tools::sg::plotter::update_primitive_box : FAIS %d : %g %g %g : %g %g %g\n",a_obj.m_FAIS,
7823// pos1.x(),pos1.y(),pos1.z(),pos2.x(),pos2.y(),pos2.z());
7824
7825 if(a_obj.m_FAIS==plottable_box::HOLLOW) {
7826
7827 separator* sep = new separator;
7828
7829 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7830 mat->color = a_obj.m_PLCI;
7831 sep->add(mat);
7832
7833 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7834 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
7835 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
7836 ds->line_width = 1;
7837 sep->add(ds);
7838
7839 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7840 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
7841 sep->add(vtxs);
7842
7843 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7844 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos1[1],z);
7845 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7846 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos2[1],z);
7847 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7848
7849 m_primitives_sep.add(sep);
7850
7851 } else if(a_obj.m_FAIS==plottable_box::SOLID) {
7852 separator* sep = new separator;
7853
7854 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7855 mat->color = a_obj.m_FACI;
7856 sep->add(mat);
7857
7858 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7859 ds->style = draw_style::filled;
7860 sep->add(ds);
7861
7862 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7863 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
7864 sep->add(vtxs);
7865
7866 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7867 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos1[1],z);
7868 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7869 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos2[1],z);
7870
7871 m_primitives_sep.add(sep);
7872
7873 } else if(a_obj.m_FAIS==plottable_box::HATCHED) {
7874
7875 {separator* sep = new separator;
7876
7877 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7878 mat->color = a_obj.m_FACI;
7879 sep->add(mat);
7880
7881 hatching_policy hatching;
7882 float spacing;
7883 float angle_right;
7884 float angle_left;
7885 PAW_hatch(a_obj.m_FASI,hatching,spacing,angle_right,angle_left);
7886 float stripWidth = 0;
7887
7888 if((hatching==hatching_right)||((hatching==hatching_left_and_right))) {
7889 rep_box_hatch(*sep,spacing,angle_right,stripWidth,pos1[0],pos1[1],pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7890 }
7891 if((hatching==hatching_left)||((hatching==hatching_left_and_right))) {
7892 rep_box_hatch(*sep,spacing,angle_left,stripWidth,pos1[0],pos1[1],pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7893 }
7894
7895 if(hatching==hatching_none) {
7896 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7897 ds->style = draw_style::filled;
7898 sep->add(ds);
7899 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7900 vtxs->mode = gl::triangle_fan();
7901 sep->add(vtxs);
7902 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7903 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos1[1],z);
7904 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7905 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos2[1],z);
7906 }
7907
7908 m_primitives_sep.add(sep);}
7909
7910 if(a_obj.m_BORD) {
7911 separator* sep = new separator;
7912 rgba* mat = new rgba();
7913 mat->color = a_obj.m_PLCI;
7914 sep->add(mat);
7915
7916 draw_style* ds = new draw_style;
7917 ds->style = draw_style::lines;
7918 ds->line_pattern = line_solid;
7919 ds->line_width = 1;
7920 sep->add(ds);
7921
7922 vertices* vtxs = new vertices;
7923 vtxs->mode = gl::line_strip();
7924 sep->add(vtxs);
7925
7926 z *= 1.01F;
7927 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7928 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos1[1],z);
7929 vtxs->add(pos2[0],pos2[1],z);
7930 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos2[1],z);
7931 vtxs->add(pos1[0],pos1[1],z);
7932
7933 m_primitives_sep.add(sep);
7934 }
7935
7936 } else if(a_obj.m_FAIS==plottable_box::PATTERN) {
7937 a_out << "tools::sg::plotter::update_plottable_box FAIS PATTERN not yet handled." << std::endl;
7938 }
7939
7940 }

7942protected: //etc
7943 // background is at z = 0.
7944 // last z items are text in infos, legend boxes that should be at xy_depth().
7945
7946 float _zoffset() const {
7947 // first data plane is at _zoffset.
7948 // last one at m_plottables.size()*_zoffset = xy_depth-_zoffset().
7949 return xy_depth.value()/(m_plottables.size()+1);
7950 }
7951 float _zaxis() const {return _zoffset();}
7952 float _zgrid() const {return xy_depth-_zoffset()*0.5f;}
7953 float _ztext() const {return 0.01f;} //if text back is visible else 0. (sf<float> zfront ?)
7954 float _zscale_text() const {return _zoffset()*0.4f/_ztext();} //title and infos boxes thickness.
7955 float _zinfos() const {return xy_depth-_zoffset()*0.4f;} //in front _zgrid
7956 float _zhatch() const {return _zoffset()*0.25f;}
7957 float _zerrors() const {return _zoffset()*0.5f;}

7960
7961 static float take_log(float a_x){
7962 if(a_x<=0) {
7963 return -FLT_MAX;
7964 } else {
7965 return flog10(a_x);
7966 }
7967 }
7968
7969 static float verify_log(float aVal,float aMin,float aDx,bool aLog){
7970 if(aLog) {
7971 if(aVal>0.0F) {
7972 return (flog10(aVal) - aMin)/aDx;
7973 } else { // Return a negative large number :
7974 //return -FLT_MAX;
7975 return -100;
7976 }
7977 } else {
7978 // Simple protection against value that could exceed a float :
7979 if(aVal>(aMin+100.0F * aDx)) return 100;
7980 if(aVal<aMin-100.0F * aDx) return -100;
7981 // Rescale :
7982 return (aVal - aMin)/aDx;
7983 }
7984 }
7985
7986 static float verify_log_inv(float aVal,float aMin,float aDx,bool aLog){
7987 if(aLog) {
7988 return fpow(10,aVal*aDx+aMin);
7989 } else {
7990 return aVal*aDx+aMin;
7991 }
7992 }

8105 bool first_bins(bins1D*& a_1,bins2D*& a_2) const {
8106 std::vector<plottable*>::const_iterator it;
8107 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();++it) {
8108 plottable* object = *it;
8109 if(!object) continue;
8110 if(bins1D* b1 = safe_cast<plottable,bins1D>(*object)) {
8111 a_1 = b1;
8112 a_2 = 0;
8113 return true;
8114 } else if(bins2D* b2 = safe_cast<plottable,bins2D>(*object)) {
8115 a_1 = 0;
8116 a_2 = b2;
8117 return true;
8118 }
8119 }
8120 a_1 = 0;
8121 a_2 = 0;
8122 return false;
8123 }
8124
8125 bool first_func(func1D*& a_1,func2D*& a_2) const {
8126 std::vector<plottable*>::const_iterator it;
8127 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();++it) {
8128 plottable* object = *it;
8129 if(!object) continue;
8130 if(func1D* f1 = safe_cast<plottable,func1D>(*object)) {
8131 a_1 = f1;
8132 a_2 = 0;
8133 return true;
8134 } else if(func2D* f2 = safe_cast<plottable,func2D>(*object)) {
8135 a_1 = 0;
8136 a_2 = f2;
8137 return true;
8138 }
8139 }
8140 a_1 = 0;
8141 a_2 = 0;
8142 return false;
8143 }
8144
8145 bool first_points(points2D*& a_2,points3D*& a_3) const {
8146 std::vector<plottable*>::const_iterator it;
8147 for(it=m_plottables.begin();it!=m_plottables.end();++it) {
8148 plottable* object = *it;
8149 if(!object) continue;
8150 if(points2D* p2 = safe_cast<plottable,points2D>(*object)) {
8151 a_2 = p2;
8152 a_3 = 0;
8153 return true;
8154 } else if(points3D* p3 = safe_cast<plottable,points3D>(*object)) {
8155 a_2 = 0;
8156 a_3 = p3;
8157 return true;
8158 }
8159 }
8160 a_2 = 0;
8161 a_3 = 0;
8162 return false;
8163 }

8180
8181 static void add_pt(std::vector<float>& a_pts,float a_x,float a_y,float a_z){
8182 a_pts.push_back(a_x);
8183 a_pts.push_back(a_y);
8184 a_pts.push_back(a_z);
8185 }
8186
8187 static void clip_points_2D(const std::vector<vec3f>& a_points,
8188 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,std::vector<float>& a_pts) {
8189 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
8190 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
8191 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
8192
8193 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
8194 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
8195 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
8196
8197 a_pts.clear();
8198
8199 float xx,yy,zz;
8200 tools_vforcit(vec3f,a_points,it) {
8201 const vec3f& _point = *it;
8202 xx = _point[0];
8203 yy = _point[1];
8204 zz = _point[2];
8205 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
8206 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
8207 if((xx>=0)&&(xx<=1)&&(yy>=0)&&(yy<=1)) add_pt(a_pts,xx,yy,zz);
8208 }
8209 }
8210
8211 static void clip_polyline_2D(const std::vector<vec3f>& a_points,
8212 const rep_box& a_box_x,const rep_box& a_box_y,std::vector<float>& a_pts) {
8213 // Clip line in a_box_x, a_box_y.
8214
8215 //NOTE : it is not a general algorithm.
8216 // It is assumed that a_points are ordered with increasing x.
8217 // And the algorithm clips against up and bottom BoxY lines.
8218 // (Use clip<float> for a more general algorithm ?)
8219
8220 float xmin = a_box_x.m_pos;
8221 float dx = a_box_x.m_width;
8222 bool xlog = a_box_x.m_log;
8223
8224 float ymin = a_box_y.m_pos;
8225 float dy = a_box_y.m_width;
8226 bool ylog = a_box_y.m_log;
8227
8228 a_pts.clear();
8229
8230 float xprev = 0;
8231 float yprev = 0;
8232
8233 {unsigned int index = 0;
8234 std::vector<vec3f>::const_iterator it;
8235 for(it=a_points.begin();it!=a_points.end();++it,index++) {
8236 const vec3f& _point = *it;
8237 float xx = _point[0];
8238 float yy = _point[1];
8239 float zz = _point[2];
8240 //add_pt(a_pts,xx,yy,zz);continue; //debug
8241 xx = verify_log(xx,xmin,dx,xlog);
8242 yy = verify_log(yy,ymin,dy,ylog);
8243 if((xx>=0)&&(xx<=1) ) {
8244 if(yy>1) {
8245 if(index==0) {
8246 add_pt(a_pts,xx,1,zz);
8247 } else {
8248 if(yprev>1) {
8249 add_pt(a_pts,xx,1,zz);
8250 } else if(yprev<0) {
8251 float a = (yy - yprev)/(xx - xprev);
8252 float b = yy - a * xx;
8253 add_pt(a_pts,-b/a,0,zz);
8254 add_pt(a_pts,(1 - b)/a,1,zz);
8255 add_pt(a_pts,xx,1,zz);
8256 } else {
8257 float a = (yy - yprev)/(xx - xprev);
8258 float b = yy - a * xx;
8259 add_pt(a_pts,(1 - b)/a,1,zz);
8260 add_pt(a_pts,xx,1,zz);
8261 }
8262 }
8263 } else if (yy < 0) {
8264 if(index==0) {
8265 add_pt(a_pts,xx,0,zz);
8266 } else {
8267 if(yprev<0) {
8268 add_pt(a_pts,xx,0,zz);
8269 } else if(yprev>1) {
8270 float a = (yy - yprev)/(xx - xprev);
8271 float b = yy - a * xx;
8272 add_pt(a_pts,(1 - b)/a,1,zz);
8273 add_pt(a_pts,-b/a,0,zz);
8274 add_pt(a_pts,xx,0,zz);
8275 } else {
8276 float a = (yy - yprev)/(xx - xprev);
8277 float b = yy - a * xx;
8278 add_pt(a_pts,-b/a,0,zz);
8279 add_pt(a_pts,xx,0,zz);
8280 }
8281 }
8282 } else {
8283 if(index==0) {
8284 add_pt(a_pts,xx,yy,zz);
8285 } else if( (yprev>1) || (yprev<0) ) {
8286 // interpolate :
8287 float a = (yy - yprev)/(xx - xprev);
8288 float b = yy - a * xx;
8289 if(yprev>1) {
8290 add_pt(a_pts,(1 - b)/a,1,zz);
8291 } else {
8292 add_pt(a_pts,-b/a,0,zz);
8293 }
8294 add_pt(a_pts,xx,yy,zz);
8295 } else {
8296 add_pt(a_pts,xx,yy,zz);
8297 }
8298 }
8299 }
8300 xprev = xx;
8301 yprev = yy;
8302 }}
8303 }
8304
8305 bool sto(const std::string& a_s,vec2f& a_v) {
8306 std::vector<std::string> ws;
8307 words(a_s," ",false,ws);
8308 if(ws.size()!=2) return false;
8309 float x = 0;
8310 if(!to<float>(ws[0],x)) return false;
8311 float y = 0;
8312 if(!to<float>(ws[1],x)) return false;
8313 a_v.set_value(x,y);
8314 return true;
8315 }
8316
8317 bool sto(const std::string& a_s,unit_type& a_v) {
8318 if(a_s=="percent") {a_v = unit_percent;return true;}
8319 else if(a_s=="axis") {a_v = unit_axis;return true;}
8320 return false;
8321 }
8322
8323 void clear_cmaps() {
8324 {std::vector<base_colormap*>::iterator it;
8325 for(it=m_bins_cmaps.begin();it!=m_bins_cmaps.end();++it) delete *it;
8326 m_bins_cmaps.clear();}
8327
8328 {std::vector<base_colormap*>::iterator it;
8329 for(it=m_points_cmaps.begin();it!=m_points_cmaps.end();++it) delete *it;
8330 m_points_cmaps.clear();}
8331
8332 {std::vector<base_colormap*>::iterator it;
8333 for(it=m_func_cmaps.begin();it!=m_func_cmaps.end();++it) delete *it;
8334 m_func_cmaps.clear();}
8335 }
8336
8337 void bar_chart(float a_bar_offset,float a_bar_width,
8338 float& a_beg,float& a_end){
8339 float xe = (a_end - a_beg)*a_bar_offset;
8340 float xw = (a_end - a_beg)*a_bar_width;
8341 a_end = a_beg + xe + xw;
8342 a_beg = a_beg + xe;
8343 }
